Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:50.91,6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,500)\fs62.486\fn方正小标宋简体\pos(975,554.946)}{\c&HD9D9D9&\t(0,3000,\c&HFFFFFF&)}致命魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得足够仔细吗\N{\fs40.9}Are you watching closely?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个魔术都由三个部分 或者说是三个步骤组成\N{\fs40.9}Every magic trick consists of three parts, or acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一部分叫"暗度陈仓"\N{\fs40.9}The first part is called "The pledge."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师向你展示某个看似平常的物件\N{\fs40.9}The magician shows you something ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副牌 一只鸟 或一个人\N{\fs40.9}A deck of cards, a bird or a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他向你展示这个物件\N{\fs40.9}He shows you this object.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还会请你去检查一番\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps he asks you to inspect it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看它是否藏有猫腻\N{\fs40.9}to see that it is indeed real,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否动过手脚 \N{\fs40.9}unaltered, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当然 其中肯定暗藏门道\N{\fs40.9}But, of course, it probably isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你往哪儿走呢\N{\fs40.9}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这演出的一份子 蠢货\N{\fs40.9}I'm part of the bloody act, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二部分叫做"风云变色"\N{\fs40.9}The second act is called "The turn."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师让那个看似平常的东西\N{\fs40.9}The magician takes the ordinary something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现出非同寻常的效果\N{\fs40.9}and makes it do something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你肯定很想弄清其中奥义 但你不会如愿的\N{\fs40.9}Now you're looking for the secret, but you won't find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很显然 你并没有仔细观看\N{\fs40.9}because, of course, you're not really looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是真的想把它弄清楚\N{\fs40.9}You don't really want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望被愚弄\N{\fs40.9}You want to be... fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此时你还不会为之鼓掌\N{\fs40.9}But you wouldn't clap yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为把东西变没并没有什么了不起\N{\fs40.9}because making something disappear isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的是能再把它变回来\N{\fs40.9}You have to bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此所有的魔术还包括这第三个部分\N{\fs40.9}That's why every magic trick has a third act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它最难参透\N{\fs40.9}The hardest part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一步我们称其为\N{\fs40.9}The part we call...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"拨云见日"\N{\fs40.9}..."the prestige."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拨云见日\N{\fs40.9}The prestige?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那天晚上 你的雇主 罗伯特 安吉尔 也就是所谓"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}And did Robert Angier, the Great Danton, your employer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的演出进行到这最后一部分了吗\N{\fs40.9}get to that final part of his trick that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 先生 途中出了意外\N{\fs40.9}No, sir. Something went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意外\N{\fs40.9}What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到有人向后台走去\N{\fs40.9}I saw someone making their way below stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我跟在他后面\N{\fs40.9}I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人是波顿 他眼睁睁看着安吉尔先生淹死\N{\fs40.9}It was Borden, watching Mr. Angier drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以向陪审团介绍一下\N{\fs40.9}Would you please describe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做什么职业的吗 卡特先生\N{\fs40.9}your occupation to the jury, Mr. Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一名道具师 \N{\fs40.9}I'm an ingenieur,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为魔术设计特效\N{\fs40.9}I design illusions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且为魔术表演建造道具\N{\fs40.9}and construct the apparatus necessary for performing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 卡特先生 当时那个舞台下面装满水的水箱\N{\fs40.9}So, Mr. Cutter, was this water-filled tank beneath the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了达成安吉尔先生的节目效果吗\N{\fs40.9}part of Mr. Angier's illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 水箱只用于第一个魔术的表演\N{\fs40.9}No. The tank was brought on for the first trick
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就被搬到台下去了\N{\fs40.9}and then taken offstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水箱肯定是在第一个节目结束后 \N{\fs40.9}Borden must have placed it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被波顿搬到活板门下面的\N{\fs40.9}under the trap door after the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个水箱有多大\N{\fs40.9}How large was this tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是用来表演水下逃生的普通水箱\N{\fs40.9}It's a normal tank for escape under water,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容积大概400到500加仑\N{\fs40.9}about 400 or 500 gallons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你认为波顿先生是如何在不被人看到的情况下\N{\fs40.9}How do you think Mr.Borden was able to move the tank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把水箱搬到活板门下面的呢\N{\fs40.9}under the trap door without anyone noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是魔术师 问他去吧\N{\fs40.9}He's a magician, ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再问一次\N{\fs40.9}I ask again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人到底会不会向我们解释安吉尔先生魔术效果的操作机制\N{\fs40.9}would this man explain the mechanics of Mr. Angier's illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"瞬间转移"魔术的机密\N{\fs40.9}The Real Transported Man
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在业内是最抢手的\N{\fs40.9}is one of the most sought after illusions in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有权将此机密出售\N{\fs40.9}I have the right to sell it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我在这儿揭秘 那这个魔术就一文不值了\N{\fs40.9}If I reveal the method here, then the trick is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们怎么能知道那个水箱的存在不是 \N{\fs40.9}How then can we know that the tank wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们自己哪一步出了问题\N{\fs40.9}simply some part of the trick that went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特先生 我理解你的难处\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Cutter, I see your predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但阿尔弗雷德·波顿现在命悬一线\N{\fs40.9}But Alfred Borden's life hangs in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能私下里向我揭晓其中奥秘\N{\fs40.9}If you were prepared to disclose the details to me in private,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能使我明了水箱和魔术的关联 方便判案\N{\fs40.9}I might be able to judge their relevance to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能接受这样折中的方法吗\N{\fs40.9}Might this be an acceptable compromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把您的口袋都清空\N{\fs40.9}I'm going to have to ask you to turn out your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想这么做 先生 \N{\fs40.9}Not my idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监狱长去年看了他在曼彻斯特的演出\N{\fs40.9}The warden saw his show in Manchester last year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他上演了一出凭空消失\N{\fs40.9}where he vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定会想尽方法逃跑\N{\fs40.9}He's convinced he'll try and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过他 波顿逃不掉的\N{\fs40.9}I told him the only way Borden's going to disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非让他跟其他犯人住一起\N{\fs40.9}is if I leave him out there with the other inmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查锁扣\N{\fs40.9}Check the locks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查两次\N{\fs40.9}...twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫欧文斯\N{\fs40.9}My name is Owens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一名律师\N{\fs40.9}I'm a solicitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的委托人是卡德罗勋爵 他是一个业余魔术师\N{\fs40.9}I represent Lord Caldlow, an accomplished amateur magician and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱\N{\fs40.9}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 卡德罗勋爵对你的  - 他出多少钱买我的魔术\N{\fs40.9}- Lord Caldlow is interested... - How much for my tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五千镑\N{\fs40.9}Five thousand pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟法隆谈 他是我的道具师 把钱给他\N{\fs40.9}Talk to Fallon, my ingenieur. Money's for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他谈了 他提出把你的魔术都卖给我\N{\fs40.9}Yes, I did. He offered to sell me your tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了最值钱的那一个 "瞬间转移"魔术\N{\fs40.9}All except the most valuable one, The Transported Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我把自己最伟大的魔术卖掉 我永远都不会原谅我自己\N{\fs40.9}Well, I won't forgive myself for selling my greatest trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是为了你的女儿呢\N{\fs40.9}Even for your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果确实是像报纸上说的那样 你会被绞死\N{\fs40.9}If the newspapers are right, and you are for the drop,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的女儿就没人照顾了\N{\fs40.9}your daughter is going to need looking after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法隆会照顾她\N{\fs40.9}Fallon will take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了 法隆\N{\fs40.9}Perfect, Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身世跟你一样是个谜\N{\fs40.9}A man with a past as obscure as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭已经决议 你的女儿不能让他监管\N{\fs40.9}The courts have motioned that the girl has be removed from his care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的女儿会成为孤儿\N{\fs40.9}Now the girl will be an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你对济贫院不陌生\N{\fs40.9}I know you're no stranger to the workhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿跟这里的条件比起来怎么样\N{\fs40.9}It's better than here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在给你机会 让你有尊严地料理后事\N{\fs40.9}I'm offering you a way to wrap up your affairs with dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在给你机会 让你的女儿有个好的未来\N{\fs40.9}I'm offering your daughter a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在卡德罗勋爵的监护下 她将应有尽有\N{\fs40.9}As Lord Caldlow's ward, she will want for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不愁\N{\fs40.9}...ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想吧\N{\fs40.9}Well, think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡德罗勋爵让我把这个交给你\N{\fs40.9}And Lord Caldlow would like you to have this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显示他的诚意 他觉得你应该会对这个有兴趣\N{\fs40.9}as a show of good faith. He thought it might be of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是罗伯特·安吉尔的日记 \N{\fs40.9}It's Robert Angier's diary,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面包括他在科罗拉多那段时间是怎么学成你的魔术的\N{\fs40.9}including the time he spent in Colorado learning your trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他从来没学成过我的魔术  - 真的吗\N{\fs40.9}- He never learned my trick. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从科罗拉多回来后 演出了全新版本的"瞬间转移"\N{\fs40.9}On his return from Colorado, he mounted a version of The Transported Man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸上说比你的原版好多了\N{\fs40.9}that the papers said was better even than your original.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是想知道安吉尔的秘密\N{\fs40.9}If you want Angier's secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把他挖出来自己问吧\N{\fs40.9}you go dig him up and ask him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你的秘密 波顿先生\N{\fs40.9}I want your secret, Mr. Borden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想你的女儿\N{\fs40.9}Consider your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密码\N{\fs40.9}A cipher,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谜团\N{\fs40.9}an enigma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探寻\N{\fs40.9}...A search,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探寻问题的答案\N{\fs40.9}a search for answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使科罗拉多是我旅行的终点\N{\fs40.9}Even if Colorado is the end of my journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要解开波顿的秘密 \N{\fs40.9}it'll take much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定还要花费相当长的一段时间\N{\fs40.9}to unravel the rest of Borden's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他笔记本里的密码可以通过一个关键词解开\N{\fs40.9}See, the cipher in his notebook is unlocked by a single word,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要把他的文字全部翻译好 弄清他的意图\N{\fs40.9}but it will still take months to translate his writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要花费数月\N{\fs40.9}And to know his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务有多艰巨 我的热情就有多高涨\N{\fs40.9}Well, my passion is equal to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:31.27,1,,0,0,0,,{\fs56.806\b1\fn微软雅黑\c&H311F0D&\pos(981,293.517)\frx12\fry348\frz5.259}科罗拉多泉{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔先生 欢迎来到科罗拉多泉\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Angier, welcome to Colorado Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 整个镇都通电了  - 是的\N{\fs40.9}- The whole town has electricity. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs40.9}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接待可真隆重\N{\fs40.9}...quite a reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是我们本季的第一位客人 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}You're our first guest of the season, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在电报里没有说要在这儿住多久\N{\fs40.9}Your telegram didn't indicate how long you'd be staying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多久住多久\N{\fs40.9}As long as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一位向导明天带我上山\N{\fs40.9}I will need a coach tomorrow to take me up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山顶现在闲人免进 先生\N{\fs40.9}Well, the peak's closed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在做科学实验\N{\fs40.9}For scientific experimentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs40.9}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才到这儿来\N{\fs40.9}That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕接下来您得自己走了 先生\N{\fs40.9}You'll have to walk the rest, I'm afraid, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.62,2,,0,0,0,,{\frz355.2\fs45.444\b1\fn微软雅黑\c&H040742&\pos(303.6,419.929)}极度危险{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.62,2,,0,0,0,,{\fs45.444\b1\fn微软雅黑\c&H070740&\pos(982.8,554.7)}有电危险{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.62,2,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs45.444\b1\c&H04043F&\frz356.7\frx4\fry356\pos(1603.2,496.893)}严禁擅自入内{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人惊讶 你们这些报社记者都不认字吗\N{\fs40.9}I'm amazed how many of you newspaper writers can't read my sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会用这种方式迎接客人\N{\fs40.9}Not the welcome I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁\N{\fs40.9}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}You're the Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在伦敦看过你的演出\N{\fs40.9}I saw your show in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连着七次猜中了观众的口袋里装的所有东西\N{\fs40.9}Seven times you guessed every object the audience had in their pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿利 对栅栏的事说声抱歉\N{\fs40.9}I'm Alley. Sorry about the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是有人来打扰我们工作\N{\fs40.9}People keep interfering with our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来找特斯拉的\N{\fs40.9}I've come to see Tesla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs40.9}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前为我的一位同事造过一台机器\N{\fs40.9}He made a machine for a colleague of mine some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能为我引见他吗\N{\fs40.9}Can you get me a meeting with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不可能\N{\fs40.9}Impossible, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了很多钱\N{\fs40.9}I've brought a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的帮不了你\N{\fs40.9}I simply can't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直住在那个酒店里\N{\fs40.9}I'll be staying at the hotel, indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 猜我现在手上拿着什么\N{\fs40.9}Hey, what am I holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表\N{\fs40.9}Your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿的日记最早记录的是1897年4月3日\N{\fs40.9}Borden's journal entry for April 3, 1897,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在欧菲姆剧院的一场演出\N{\fs40.9}describes a show at the Orpheum Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时他才刚认识我没几天\N{\fs40.9}That was just days after he first met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是两个有着大好前途的年轻小伙\N{\fs40.9}We were two young men at the start of a great career,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们潜心研究魔术\N{\fs40.9}two young men devoted to an illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未想过伤害别人\N{\fs40.9}two young men who never intended to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁愿意到台上来绑住这位美丽姑娘的手脚\N{\fs40.9}Which of you brave souls is willing to bind this lovely young woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs40.9}Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你绑住她的双手\N{\fs40.9}If you would tie her wrists,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑住她的双脚\N{\fs40.9}bind her feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绳子在脚踝绕一圈\N{\fs40.9}...around the ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩有谁是水手吗\N{\fs40.9}Are either of you two gentlemen sailors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不是  - 不是\N{\fs40.9}- No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩肯定都能打个结实的结\N{\fs40.9}I'm sure you can both tie a strong knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骄傲自大 毫无新意 无聊透顶\N{\fs40.9}He's complacent, he's predictable, he's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在米尔顿做出了成绩 先不管这成绩怎么样吧\N{\fs40.9}I mean, Milton has gotten success, whatever that means,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他害怕了 不敢再冒险了\N{\fs40.9}so now he's scared. He won't take any risks at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众对他充满期待 他却用他那老套 二流的戏法\N{\fs40.9}I mean, he's squandering the goodwill of his audience with his tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去糊弄他们  - 观众就好这口\N{\fs40.9}- second-rate tricks... - They're all favorites, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好这口 拜托 来点新鲜的行不行 \N{\fs40.9}Favorites? Come on. Give me something fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至连空手抓子弹都不敢\N{\fs40.9}He won't even try a bloody bullet catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手抓子弹简直就是自杀\N{\fs40.9}A bullet catch is suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是正好碰上个机灵鬼\N{\fs40.9}All it takes is some smartass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往枪管里装个纽扣 那就完了\N{\fs40.9}volunteer to put a button in the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 找个托啊  - 你又不能每个魔术都找托儿\N{\fs40.9}- Use a plant. - You can't use a plant for every trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的观众都要没位置坐了\N{\fs40.9}No seats left for the punters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 不弄空手抓子弹\N{\fs40.9}All right, no bullet catch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但重点是 真正的魔术师会探索新的魔术 \N{\fs40.9}whatever, but the point is a real magician tries to invent something new
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探索其他魔术师想破脑袋都想不通的新魔术\N{\fs40.9}that other magicians will scratch their heads over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就可以把这魔术的秘诀卖给他 赚笔小钱了\N{\fs40.9}Then you sell it to him for a small fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 我猜你肯定会这样的魔术吧 波顿先生\N{\fs40.9}- What? - I suppose you have such a trick, Mr. Borden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 你介意把它卖给我吗\N{\fs40.9}- I sure do. - Would you care to sell it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意 我的魔术任何人都学不来\N{\fs40.9}No. No one else can do my trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 任何魔术都可以被复制 对吧 卡特先生  - 错\N{\fs40.9}- Any trick can be duplicated, right, Mr. Cutter - Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说波顿先生有自己的魔术大作\N{\fs40.9}If Mr. Borden has invented his masterpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他就随时能去演出\N{\fs40.9}he's prepared to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔顿是个经验丰富的表演者 但波顿说得对\N{\fs40.9}Milton is a skilled showman, but Borden is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不会弄脏他的手的\N{\fs40.9}he won't get his hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们真想看一个真正的魔术师需要付出的代价\N{\fs40.9}If you want to see what it takes to make real magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去田利剧院吧 \N{\fs40.9}go to the Tenley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个中国人在那儿表演 他是有真功夫的\N{\fs40.9}There's a chinaman there and he really has what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 程连苏  - 那儿票太贵 我买不起\N{\fs40.9}- Chung Ling Soo. - Tickets are pricey. I can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识那儿看门的人\N{\fs40.9}I know the bloke run the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个去看他的演出\N{\fs40.9}You two go and see that show,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来之后 谁能告诉我他的金鱼缸魔术是怎么变的  \N{\fs40.9}and whichever one of you can tell me how he does the goldfish bowl trick
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他奖励\N{\fs40.9}gets the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么奖励  - 奖励是跟我的老朋友\N{\fs40.9}- Which is? - Ten minutes onstage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿克曼先生同台十分钟的机会\N{\fs40.9}with my old friend, Mr. Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 当真  - 谁是阿克曼\N{\fs40.9}- Really? - Who's Ackerman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦敦最好的剧院经纪人\N{\fs40.9}The top theatrical agent in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我看见你又打了松结  - 应该是我自己转了下手腕弄的\N{\fs40.9}- I saw you drop the knot again. - I think I turned my wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时候就是会犯糊涂 对不对\N{\fs40.9}Some nights you just don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果朱莉娅在吊起来的时候绳结松开了\N{\fs40.9}I mean, if that knot slips and Julia's on the hoist,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会摔断腿的\N{\fs40.9}she'll break her leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就不应该打这样的结\N{\fs40.9}It's the wrong knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就说过 蓝式双结会绑得更结实\N{\fs40.9}Like I said, the Langford double will hold tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝式双结一旦浸水 会很危险\N{\fs40.9}The Langford double isn't a wet knot. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果绳子泡水涨开 她是解不开的\N{\fs40.9}If the rope swells, she won't be able to slip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我能在水下解开蓝式双结  - 她能解开 我们多练几次就行了\N{\fs40.9}- I can slip a Langford underwater. - She can slip it. We can practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿 他说了不行  \N{\fs40.9}Borden, he said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你对绳结倒是比我了解还清楚咯\N{\fs40.9}Oh, well, you know knots better than me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 不准再出错\N{\fs40.9}Listen, no more mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你呢 你想继续吗\N{\fs40.9}All right. Yeah? Do you? You want to take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你走吧  - 我可不这么想\N{\fs40.9}- Just leave. - I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 卡特 这小子哪儿来的\N{\fs40.9}Hey, Cutter, where's he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不问你是从哪儿来的 他本来是给维吉尔在剧院大厅搬道具的\N{\fs40.9}Where are you from? He shifts props for Virgil at the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不担心他会偷学你的魔术吗  \N{\fs40.9}Aren't you worried he'll steal your tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会这么做的\N{\fs40.9}He doesn't deal in methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道  \N{\fs40.9}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我雇他来 是为了弄清楚维吉尔的那个桔子魔术是怎么变的\N{\fs40.9}Because I hired him to find out how Virgil does the orange trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我不信任他  - 他是个天生的魔术师\N{\fs40.9}- I don't trust him. - He's a natural magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当然无法信任他\N{\fs40.9}'Course you can't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他还好啊\N{\fs40.9}I think he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你觉得每个人都还好  - 包括你\N{\fs40.9}- You think everyone's all right. - Even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔 注意你在台上的一举一动 \N{\fs40.9}Angier, watch your sightlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我每天晚上能看到你在台上偷亲你妻子的腿\N{\fs40.9}If I can see you kiss your wife's leg every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那说明三四排尽头的观众同样看得到\N{\fs40.9}so can the blokes at the ends of rows three and four!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了 做不到的\N{\fs40.9}You're wrong. It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他  \N{\fs40.9}Look at the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是其中奥妙\N{\fs40.9}This is the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的表演 就在眼前\N{\fs40.9}This is the performance. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没有人能成功解析他的魔术\N{\fs40.9}This is why no one can detect his method.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是对艺术的献身\N{\fs40.9}Total devotion to his art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全的自我牺牲\N{\fs40.9}A lot of self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂吗\N{\fs40.9}You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样才能逃离\N{\fs40.9}It's the only way to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切 懂吗\N{\fs40.9}...all this, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本抬不动这东西 而且它里面还没装水\N{\fs40.9}I can barely lift this thing and it's not even filled with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也没有鱼 看\N{\fs40.9}Or fish, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚 稍等一下\N{\fs40.9}I don't know. Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定跟头牛一样壮\N{\fs40.9}He must be strong as an ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这几年来都在假装残疾\N{\fs40.9}He's been pretending to be a cripple for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他在公共场合 只要他外出 他就会如此 简直无法想象\N{\fs40.9}Any time he's in public, any time he goes out. It's unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿当时一下就看穿了 但我无法做到像他一样\N{\fs40.9}Borden saw it at once. But I couldn't fathom it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子伪装成另一个人的样子\N{\fs40.9}Living my whole life pretending to be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就是在伪装别人啊\N{\fs40.9}You are pretending to be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改名字不算吧\N{\fs40.9}I don't think changing a name compares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你改的不仅仅是你的名字 还包括你的身世\N{\fs40.9}Not just your name. It's who you are and where you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我答应过家人\N{\fs40.9}Cos I promised my family I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会用变戏法这等事来让家族脸上无光\N{\fs40.9}embarrass them with my theatrical endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你想了一个名字\N{\fs40.9}I thought of a name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}The Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗 这个名字多么经典\N{\fs40.9}Do you like it? But it's sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是法国名字吧\N{\fs40.9}It's French.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读着波顿的日记\N{\fs40.9}Borden writes as if no one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他仿佛认为世界上独他一人懂得魔术的真正奥义\N{\fs40.9}but he understood the true nature of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他怎么会懂得什么叫自我牺牲\N{\fs40.9}But what does he know of self-sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个该死的蠢货\N{\fs40.9}You bloody fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他杀死了小鸟  - 没事\N{\fs40.9}- He killed it. - It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他杀死了小鸟  - 他没有\N{\fs40.9}- He killed it. - He didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 他要把它变回来了\N{\fs40.9}See, now he'll bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 他杀了它  - 不 他没有\N{\fs40.9}- No, he killed it. - No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这儿 他没事儿 他好着呢\N{\fs40.9}Look, see, he's all right. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 看  - 可它的兄弟哪儿去了\N{\fs40.9}- Look at him. - But where's his brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子真聪明\N{\fs40.9}He's a sharp lad, your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我侄子\N{\fs40.9}Oh, he's... he's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs40.9}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你是走运的那个\N{\fs40.9}You're the lucky one today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得足够仔细吗\N{\fs40.9}Are you watching closely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再仔细看\N{\fs40.9}Look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远别把这个给别人看\N{\fs40.9}Never show anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为了搞清楚其中的奥秘会求你 拍你的马屁\N{\fs40.9}They'll beg you and they'll flatter you for the secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦你把它说出来 你对他们就一文不值了\N{\fs40.9}but as soon as you give it up, you'll be nothing to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗 一文不值\N{\fs40.9}You understand? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会为魔术的奥秘感到惊艳\N{\fs40.9}The secret impresses no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魔术表演才是真正大放异彩的东西\N{\fs40.9}The trick you use it for is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你请的午饭 波顿先生\N{\fs40.9}Well, thank you for lunch, Mr. Borden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fs40.9}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔佛雷德 叫我阿尔佛雷德\N{\fs40.9}Alfred, it's Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔佛雷德\N{\fs40.9}Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能进去喝杯茶吗\N{\fs40.9}Since I come, I could use a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不能 房东会说闲话的 恐怕\N{\fs40.9}I just can't allow... It's the landlord. It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为凭这个锁就能把我隔在门外了吗\N{\fs40.9}You think that's... Is that enough to keep me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看可以\N{\fs40.9}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 咱们再会咯\N{\fs40.9}So I'll see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加奶和糖吗\N{\fs40.9}Milk and sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是什么\N{\fs40.9}What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔的机器\N{\fs40.9}Angier's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.14,2,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.61\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs79.527\c&H020229&\3c&H0B2333&\pos(671.4,561.192)\clip(m 456 511.25 l 846 460.125 861 530.5 480 582.75)}科罗拉多泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你造的吗 卡特先生\N{\fs40.9}You built this, Mr. Cutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不 先生 这个不是魔术师造的\N{\fs40.9}Oh, no, sir. This wasn't built by a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是由一个巫师造出来的\N{\fs40.9}This was built by a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师的魔术是假的 但他的法术是真的\N{\fs40.9}A man who can actually do what magicians pretend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我 法官大人\N{\fs40.9}Tell me, Your Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判后这些东西会怎么处理\N{\fs40.9}what happens with these things after the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡德罗勋爵买下了它们\N{\fs40.9}They've been sold to a Lord Caldlow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个热心肠的收藏家 对这个案子很有兴趣\N{\fs40.9}An avid collector, very interested in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 千万别让他把这个拿走\N{\fs40.9}Yeah. Well, don't let him take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 太危险了\N{\fs40.9}- Why ever not? - It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜 尽管它的外表华丽雄伟 \N{\fs40.9}I'm sure beneath its bells and whistles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它能变的戏法却很低级 令人失望吧\N{\fs40.9}it's got a simple and disappointing trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它最令人失望之处 先生\N{\fs40.9}The most disappointing of all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在于它所变的并非魔术\N{\fs40.9}It has no trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而都真切存在\N{\fs40.9}It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个水箱就是使安吉尔淹死的那个吗\N{\fs40.9}This is the tank Angier drowned in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40.9}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个洞口\N{\fs40.9}This is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演者可以把手伸出来\N{\fs40.9}...place where the performer's hand reaches through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开魔术锁\N{\fs40.9}to the trick padlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是典型的逃生魔术道具吧\N{\fs40.9}A standard magical apparatus for escapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但有一点不一样\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, with one important difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个锁不是魔术锁\N{\fs40.9}This isn't a trick lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被人换成了真正的锁\N{\fs40.9}It's been switched for a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟用这种方法来杀人\N{\fs40.9}What a way to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是魔术师 法官大人\N{\fs40.9}They're magicians, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是表演者 他们通过粉饰平凡甚至残忍的真相\N{\fs40.9}Showmen, men who live by dressing up plain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来博取眼球\N{\fs40.9}and sometimes brutal truths,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们以此为生\N{\fs40.9}to amaze, to shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有观众也如此吗\N{\fs40.9}Even without an audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说当时没有观众\N{\fs40.9}There was an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这个水箱对这两个人都有着特别的意义\N{\fs40.9}You see, this water tank was of particular significance to these two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别不堪回首的意义\N{\fs40.9}Particularly awful significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁愿意到台上来绑住这位美丽姑娘的手脚\N{\fs40.9}Which of you brave souls is willing to bind this lovely young woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你绑住她的双手\N{\fs40.9}If you would tie her wrists,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绳子在脚踝绕一圈 绑住她的双脚\N{\fs40.9}bind her feet around the ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们俩有谁是水手吗  - 不是\N{\fs40.9}- Are either of you gentlemen sailors? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩肯定都能打个结实的结\N{\fs40.9}I'm sure you can both tie a strong knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.39,0:24:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.75,0:25:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\fs40.9}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱莉娅 \N{\fs40.9}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.50,0:25:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱莉娅\N{\fs40.9}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.34,0:26:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前认识一个老水手\N{\fs40.9}I knew an old sailor once.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.27,0:26:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们告诉我 他有一次落水\N{\fs40.9}They told me he went overboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.24,0:26:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被船帆缠住了\N{\fs40.9}tangled in the sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.41,0:26:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把他救了出来\N{\fs40.9}They pulled him out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.28,0:26:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他整整咳了五分钟\N{\fs40.9}but it took him five minutes to cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.25,0:26:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说淹水的感觉\N{\fs40.9}He said it was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.35,0:26:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像回家\N{\fs40.9}...going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.53,0:26:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么 波顿\N{\fs40.9}What do you want, Borden?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.67,0:26:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节哀顺变 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry for your loss, Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打的是什么结\N{\fs40.9}Which knot did you tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直这么问自己\N{\fs40.9}I keep asking myself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.72,0:26:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 然后呢  - 然后\N{\fs40.9}- And? - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我不知道\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry, I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.39,0:27:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道\N{\fs40.9}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.73,0:27:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.63,0:27:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道\N{\fs40.9}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道\N{\fs40.9}You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.31,0:27:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43.173}阿尔弗雷德 \NAlfred?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.59,0:27:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息 我们今天预定到场地了\N{\fs40.9}Good news. We got our first booking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位先生好像是第一次见\N{\fs40.9}I don't think we've had the pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.12,0:27:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法隆先生是我的道具师  \N{\fs40.9}Mr. Fallon is my ingenieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西是从哪儿\N{\fs40.9}Where did you get all...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.01,0:27:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借的 别问了\N{\fs40.9}I had to borrow and... don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.01,0:27:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很有胆识\N{\fs40.9}He's a very enterprising soul
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.29,0:27:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说法隆先生 所以\N{\fs40.9}is... is Mr. Fallon. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.16,0:27:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们雇不起他\N{\fs40.9}We can't afford to pay him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.60,0:27:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等有了足够的观众 我们就有钱了\N{\fs40.9}The money will when we got the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.66,0:27:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在怎么办\N{\fs40.9}But what about until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.14,0:27:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挣的钱还不够我们两个人吃饭的\N{\fs40.9}What I earn, it's barely enough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.43,0:27:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs40.9}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的食物分一半给他就好\N{\fs40.9}I'll share half my food with him or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.47,0:27:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个人马上也要来分你的食物了\N{\fs40.9}You're already going to be doing that with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.51,0:27:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 你\N{\fs40.9}No. You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.48,0:27:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀孕了\N{\fs40.9}Having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.81,0:27:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天呐\N{\fs40.9}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.78,0:27:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得告诉法隆\N{\fs40.9}We should have told Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.91,0:27:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太棒了 我们要有小宝宝了\N{\fs40.9}That is great! We are having a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来\N{\fs40.9}Oh, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.26,0:28:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德 这是什么\N{\fs40.9}Alfred, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.86,0:28:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我魔术演出要用的道具\N{\fs40.9}Oh, this is just the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.11,0:28:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在演出的尾声让阿克曼惊艳一下\N{\fs40.9}to work Ackerman up at the end of my act.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.10,0:28:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你那个魔术大作吗 那个伟大的魔术\N{\fs40.9}Is it the masterpiece, the great trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.10,0:28:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 那个大作还未到时候公诸于世\N{\fs40.9}No, no, no, the world is not ready for that one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.02,0:28:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个只不过是平淡无奇\N{\fs40.9}This is just your run-of-the-mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.82,0:28:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而又令人胆战心惊的空手抓子弹\N{\fs40.9}daring, spectacular bullet catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.11,0:28:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 空手抓子弹  - 没错 不过这很安全\N{\fs40.9}- A bullet catch. - Yeah, but it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.71,0:28:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证 看\N{\fs40.9}I promise. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.38,0:28:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我开枪  \N{\fs40.9}Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.67,0:28:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你开枪\N{\fs40.9}Shoot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.72,0:28:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来嘛 对我开枪\N{\fs40.9}Go on, shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.45,0:28:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这儿来  \N{\fs40.9}Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.61,0:28:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行\N{\fs40.9}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.55,0:28:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别朝那边打 朝我开枪 不要\N{\fs40.9}No, no, not there. Shoot me here. Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.36,0:28:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fs40.9}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.30,0:28:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 告诉我你怎么做到的\N{\fs40.9}That's very good. Tell me how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.70,0:28:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不能告诉你\N{\fs40.9}No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 我不能让你去表演 阿尔弗雷德 \N{\fs40.9}Well, then you can't do it, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能去表演\N{\fs40.9}I can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 阿尔佛雷德 但我一个人养不了孩子\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry, Alfred, but I can't raise a child on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.86,0:29:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉任何人我告诉过你\N{\fs40.9}You don't tell anybody that I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.76,0:29:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 火药\N{\fs40.9}- OK. - Gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.74,0:29:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,填料\N{\fs40.9}Wadding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.54,0:29:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是子弹\N{\fs40.9}Then the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.26,0:29:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推杆\N{\fs40.9}Ramrod.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.68,0:29:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出来\N{\fs40.9}Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.74,0:29:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在开枪的一瞬间 子弹根本不在枪里\N{\fs40.9}The bullet is not even in the gun when the charge is fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.92,0:29:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了其中的奥秘 就会觉得也没什么了不起的\N{\fs40.9}Once you know, it's actually very obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.58,0:29:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我还是会\N{\fs40.9}Well, I mean, you still get...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是挺危险的\N{\fs40.9}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.11,0:29:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人表演这个魔术的时候死了呢  \N{\fs40.9}People still get killed doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么弄的\N{\fs40.9}Well, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.66,0:29:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的机灵鬼会故意把硬币或者纽扣放进枪管里\N{\fs40.9}Well, you know, I mean... You get some smartass who could put a penny or a button
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.30,0:29:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有甚者 上帝保佑 莎拉 有人会把真正的子弹放进去\N{\fs40.9}or, God forbid, Sarah, somebody could put a bullet down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.20,0:29:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别担心 别担心\N{\fs40.9}Don't worry. Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.08,0:29:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让这种事发生的\N{\fs40.9}because I'm not gonna let anything happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.50,0:29:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会好的 因为\N{\fs40.9}Everything's gonna be all right because...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.74,0:29:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很爱你\N{\fs40.9}...I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.60,0:30:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 再说一遍  - 我爱你\N{\fs40.9}- Say it again. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.71,0:30:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 今天不爱  - 什么\N{\fs40.9}- Not today. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.24,0:30:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候你说的是真话 但今天你言不由衷\N{\fs40.9}Well, some days it's not true, and today you don't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你今天更爱魔术 而不是我\N{\fs40.9}Maybe today you're more in love with magic than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.78,0:30:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把它们区别开\N{\fs40.9}I like being able to tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.49,0:30:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会让你心口如一的那些日子更有意义\N{\fs40.9}It makes the days it is true mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.33,0:30:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40.9}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.75,1,,0,0,0,,{\fs56.806\b1\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\c&H2C170B&\frz9.458\pos(147,479.414)}神\N手{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.75,1,,0,0,0,,{\fs56.806\b1\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\c&H2C170B&\frz9.458\pos(288,470.425)}教\N授{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁环 女士们先生们\N{\fs40.9}Metal rings, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.28,0:30:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 注意啦\N{\fs40.9}If there are any ladies and gentlemen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.85,0:30:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(951,812.007)}坚硬的钢铁  \N{\fs40.9}Solid metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.64,0:30:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过无数次了\N{\fs40.9}Seen that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.58,0:30:53.41,2,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs64.758\c&H02080F&\pos(435,413.496)}神\N手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.58,0:30:53.41,2,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs64.758\c&H02080F&\pos(615,413.494)}教\N授
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁扔的\N{\fs40.9}Who threw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.55,0:31:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就想看这个 对吧\N{\fs40.9}This is what you came for, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.19,0:31:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs40.9}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.79,0:31:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁自愿上来\N{\fs40.9}...who wants to volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我来  - 我\N{\fs40.9}- I do! - Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.27,0:31:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 \N{\fs40.9}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs40.9}Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.17,0:31:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就站那儿\N{\fs40.9}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.59,0:32:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你够男子气概吗 先生\N{\fs40.9}Are you man enough, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.06,0:32:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够\N{\fs40.9}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.68,0:32:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打的是什么结 波顿\N{\fs40.9}Which knot did you tie, Borden?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.95,0:32:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打的是什么结 波顿\N{\fs40.9}Which knot did you tie, Borden?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.39,0:32:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs40.9}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.64,0:32:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他过来向我要一个答案 我如实回答了他\N{\fs40.9}He came in to demand an answer, and I told him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上我彻夜难眠\N{\fs40.9}That I have fought with myself over that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半的自己一口咬定是普通的滑结\N{\fs40.9}one half of me swearing blind that I tied a simple slipknot,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.40,0:33:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一半却确信自己打的是蓝式双结\N{\fs40.9}the other half convinced that I tied the Langford double.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.84,0:33:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么也无法确定\N{\fs40.9}I can never know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.72,0:33:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会不知道\N{\fs40.9}How can he not know!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.00,0:33:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会不知道\N{\fs40.9}How can he not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.40,0:33:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定知道自己打的是什么结\N{\fs40.9}He must know what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.00,0:33:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定知道\N{\fs40.9}He must.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.06,0:33:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 疼死了\N{\fs40.9}Sarah, that bloody hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.94,0:33:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白 怎么又流血了\N{\fs40.9}I don't understand how it can be bleeding again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.30,0:33:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟刚受伤那天一样糟\N{\fs40.9}It's as bad as the day it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.56,0:33:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得再请一次医生\N{\fs40.9}We have to get a doctor back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.38,0:33:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们请不起该死的医生\N{\fs40.9}We can't afford the bloody doctor back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.04,0:33:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你把她吵醒了  - 好极了\N{\fs40.9}- You've woken her. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.70,0:33:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我得让它尽快好起来 这样我才能重新工作\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry, I need this to heal so I can get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.56,0:33:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德 面对现实吧\N{\fs40.9}Alfred, you've got to face things.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.87,0:33:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都伤成这样了 还能表演什么魔术\N{\fs40.9}What tricks can you possibly perform with this injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.33,0:33:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以表演那个拖车的魔术 还有一些小魔术\N{\fs40.9}I can do car pulls. I can do some prop tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.87,0:33:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还可以表演的 我可以表演那个我跟你说过的魔术\N{\fs40.9}I can still do that. I can do the trick I've been telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.30,0:33:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可以让我扬名天下的魔术\N{\fs40.9}The one that they're gonna remember me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.81,0:33:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs40.9}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.37,0:34:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没想到我会在酒杯底下找到答案\N{\fs40.9}I never thought I'd find an answer at the bottom of a pint glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.24,0:34:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没停止探索啊\N{\fs40.9}Hasn't stopped your looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.05,0:34:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说有人预定了一个表演场地 是一个漂亮的小剧院\N{\fs40.9}Heard about a booking. Nice little theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.98,0:34:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是一个年轻上进的魔术师  - 谁啊\N{\fs40.9}- Young, up-and-coming magician. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.88,0:34:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你  - 我 预定场地 为什么\N{\fs40.9}- You. - Me? Booking? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想重操旧业\N{\fs40.9}I want to keep on working.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.10,0:34:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但谁会雇一个在座无虚席的观众面前 \N{\fs40.9}Who's going to hire the ingenieur
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死了朱莉娅 麦卡洛的道具师呢\N{\fs40.9}that killed Julia McCullough in front of a sellout crowd at the Orpheum?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.40,0:34:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那不是你的错\N{\fs40.9}Someone who knows it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.60,0:34:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还知道这跟阿尔弗雷 波顿 \N{\fs40.9}Someone who knows Alfred borden
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.00,0:34:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他那些稀奇古怪的绳结有关\N{\fs40.9}and his repertoire of exotic knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.04,0:34:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说他在南岸\N{\fs40.9}I hear he had a spot of bad luck
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演空手抓子弹时走了霉运\N{\fs40.9}catching a bullet south of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.84,0:35:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个魔术毕竟很危险\N{\fs40.9}That's a dangerous trick, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.04,0:35:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得给窗户涂上白漆\N{\fs40.9}We'll have to whitewash the windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.55,0:35:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让外面的人知道我们在做什么 这不成问题\N{\fs40.9}confound the more curious members of the public, but it will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.84,0:35:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要一个助手\N{\fs40.9}We should see about an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.42,0:35:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经寻摸好了\N{\fs40.9}I've made some arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起好艺名了吗\N{\fs40.9}You settled on a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.54,0:35:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起好了\N{\fs40.9}Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.34,0:35:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}The Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.26,0:35:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点老套吧\N{\fs40.9}It's a bit old-fashioned, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.14,0:35:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是经典\N{\fs40.9}No, it's sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特 鸟笼魔术不能作为我们魔术表演的高潮 每个人都知道这是怎么一回事\N{\fs40.9}Cutter, the birdcage can't be our climax. Everybody knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.04,0:35:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可不一样  \N{\fs40.9}Not like this, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.52,0:35:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我可不想杀鸽子\N{\fs40.9}And I don't want to kill doves.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.60,0:35:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就别上台表演\N{\fs40.9}Then stay off the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个魔术师 又不是巫师\N{\fs40.9}You're a magician, not a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.50,0:35:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是不想弄脏手\N{\fs40.9}You got to get your hands dirty,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.89,0:35:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别想创造奇迹\N{\fs40.9}if you're going to achieve the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.76,0:35:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进到里面 温小姐\N{\fs40.9}In here, Miss Wenscombe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.99,0:35:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你钻不进去 那也就没必要见安吉尔先生了 进到右边\N{\fs40.9}No point in meeting Mr. Angier if you don't fit. On the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.63,0:36:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这有什么难的  - 这个不难\N{\fs40.9}- What's so hard about this? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.73,0:36:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做的是 到下面\N{\fs40.9}You're going... down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.07,0:36:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这个从外面看不出来  - 哦 那当然\N{\fs40.9}- And this will conceal. - Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.61,0:36:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这里收紧  - 好\N{\fs40.9}- Tighten up on there. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs40.9}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.41,0:36:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个绑到这里吗\N{\fs40.9}This ties up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.55,0:36:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这个绑在背后  - 好的\N{\fs40.9}- That ties in the back. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.02,0:36:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量屏住呼吸\N{\fs40.9}Breathe as little as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.73,0:36:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N{\fs40.9}Now, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.43,0:36:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 懂了  - 好\N{\fs40.9}- That's it. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.27,0:36:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没什么经验\N{\fs40.9}She's not experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.17,0:36:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她知道怎么表现自己\N{\fs40.9}but she knows how to present herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.28,0:36:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个漂亮的助手是转移观众注意力的最好武器\N{\fs40.9}A pretty assistant is the most effective form of misdirection.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家 女士们先生们 接下来是我的最后一个魔术\N{\fs40.9}Thank you. Ladies and gentlemen, for my final trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.38,0:36:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要两名观众上台来帮我的忙\N{\fs40.9}I will require the assistance of two volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.22,0:36:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅里特先生 您愿意赏脸吗\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Merrit, if you would oblige me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.39,0:37:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs40.9}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.73,0:37:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 放在下面  - 下面 对\N{\fs40.9}- Under? - Under, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.00,0:37:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从它的脚上绕过来\N{\fs40.9}Come around his foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.37,0:37:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 当心  - 没事\N{\fs40.9}- Careful. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.66,0:37:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 让观众把手放在这边  - 嗯\N{\fs40.9}- Your volunteer, put their hand there. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.99,0:37:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一只手放这边\N{\fs40.9}And another one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.89,0:37:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅里特先生 请把你的两只手分别放在笼子两侧 \N{\fs40.9}Mr. Merrit, if you'll place your hands on either side of the cage, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.50,0:37:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 奥利维\N{\fs40.9}Thank you, Olivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.90,0:37:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好别伤害这只小动物 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}You best not be intending to hurt this animal, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.74,0:37:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会  \N{\fs40.9}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.85,0:37:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 来\N{\fs40.9}Ready? Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.87,0:37:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一  - 二\N{\fs40.9}- One... - Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.41,0:37:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三\N{\fs40.9}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.68,0:37:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真太精彩了 卡特\N{\fs40.9}That's bloody marvelous, Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.48,0:38:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs40.9}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.75,0:38:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最棒的是这个\N{\fs40.9}And the best part is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.93,0:38:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你会让我弄脏手呢\N{\fs40.9}I thought you said I had to get my hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.43,0:38:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天也许你会走到这一步的\N{\fs40.9}Someday, perhaps you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.40,0:38:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道你有没有这个胆子\N{\fs40.9}I just had to know that you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.03,0:38:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 真的很好\N{\fs40.9}Very nice. Very nice, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.03,0:38:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖 梅里特先生 \N{\fs40.9}Thank you, Mr. Merrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没来得及夸奖您漂亮的剧院呢\N{\fs40.9}I haven't had the chance to compliment you on your beautiful theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.04,0:38:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐满观众时会更漂亮 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}It'll be a lot more beautiful when it's full, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.54,0:38:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs40.9}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.48,0:38:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都这么说 我有什么好担心的\N{\fs40.9}You all say that. Why should I worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.84,0:38:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的魔术吸引不来人 自然有人能吸引得来\N{\fs40.9}If your tricks don't get them in, somebody else's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.70,0:38:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人会来表演空手抓子弹或者水下逃生什么的\N{\fs40.9}Maybe somebody willing to do a bullet catch or a water escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.92,0:38:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是小把戏 梅里特先生\N{\fs40.9}Cheap thrills, Mr. Merrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.40,0:38:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都希望在这样的演出中看到意外 \N{\fs40.9}People hoping for an accident, likely to see one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.30,0:38:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样对您的生意有什么好处\N{\fs40.9}What would that do for your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.92,0:38:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们在这儿演一个星期 John\N{\fs40.9}You got a week, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.42,0:38:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 梅里特先生\N{\fs40.9}Thank you, Mr. Merrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.79,0:38:50.92,1,,0,0,0,,{\fs45.444\c&H03080A&\b1\fn微软雅黑\pos(1580.4,156.509)}仅此一周{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.79,0:38:50.92,1,,0,0,0,,{\fs45.444\c&H010B13&\b1\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\pos(1658.4,323.564)}伟大的丹东{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.41,0:38:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fs40.9}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.58,0:39:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐第三排的那位先生\N{\fs40.9}Uh... Sir, in the third row there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.28,0:39:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请起立向大家展示一下您的手帕\N{\fs40.9}Please stand up and show us your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.98,0:39:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我的\N{\fs40.9}This isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.85,0:39:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以把它还给\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps you'd so good to return it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.06,0:39:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐第二排靠走道的那位女士\N{\fs40.9}to the lady in the aisle of the second row.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.39,0:39:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她手上应该拿着您的手帕\N{\fs40.9}I believe she has yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.03,0:39:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 真对不起\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.68,0:39:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出错了好多次 我太紧张了\N{\fs40.9}I'm making so many mistakes. I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.77,0:39:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众反应好像不太热烈 Cutter\N{\fs40.9}The audience doesn't seem to be responding, Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.11,0:39:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看过的把戏多了\N{\fs40.9}They've seen a lot of tricks before,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.41,0:39:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这一个他们肯定没看过\N{\fs40.9}but not this next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.95,0:39:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖上布\N{\fs40.9}Cloth over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.79,0:39:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷好运吧\N{\fs40.9}Keep your fingers crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.62,0:39:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去准备庆祝香槟\N{\fs40.9}I'll have the champagne ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.82,0:40:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们看过这个对吗  - 你今晚的魔术我们都看过 伙计\N{\fs40.9}- You've seen this one before? - We've seen them all before, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.50,0:40:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把难度加大一点\N{\fs40.9}I'll make it a little harder then, shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.22,0:40:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要两个自愿的观众 一位女士和一位先生\N{\fs40.9}Two volunteers, please. A lady and a gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.02,0:40:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮我端着这个笼子\N{\fs40.9}To hold this cage with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把这个魔术以一种前所未有的形式呈现给大家\N{\fs40.9}I'll perform this feat in a manner never before seen by yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上还没有一个观众看过\N{\fs40.9}or any other audience anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士 请把一只手放在笼子的前面\N{\fs40.9}Madame, place one hand on the back of the cage,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.24,0:40:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一只手放在笼子的后面 谢谢\N{\fs40.9}one hand on the front, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 请把一只手放在笼子顶部\N{\fs40.9}Sir, one hand on the bottom of the cage
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.36,0:40:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一只手放在笼子底部\N{\fs40.9}one hand on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.40,0:40:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该把他认出来的  \N{\fs40.9}I should've spotted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:40:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要操心的事本就够多了\N{\fs40.9}You had a lot of plates going.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.00,0:40:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我看他们肯定不会再让我们表演这个魔术了  - 你说得对\N{\fs40.9}- I don't suppose they'll let us do this again. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.23,0:40:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那现在我们演出的高潮节目怎么办  - 演出\N{\fs40.9}- So, what's the climax of our show? - Show?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.74,0:40:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不用再来演出了  \N{\fs40.9}You don't have a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.87,0:40:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅里特先生 您跟我们约好了一个星期的\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Merrit, we have a week's engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.94,0:40:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你们来是来表演魔术 不是让你们屠杀小鸟 \N{\fs40.9}To perform magic, not butcher birds
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.07,0:40:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者夹断客人手指的\N{\fs40.9}and break my customers' fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.61,0:41:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾收拾快走 东西不拿走就明早烧掉\N{\fs40.9}Clear out, anything here in the morning gets burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.38,0:41:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 梅里特先生  - 没什么好说的了 John\N{\fs40.9}- Mr. Merrit... - It's done, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.88,0:41:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请了一个喜剧演员来表演 你知道我有多讨厌喜剧演员的\N{\fs40.9}I've hired a comedian. You know I hate comedians.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.82,0:41:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好剧院多的是\N{\fs40.9}Well, there's plenty of good theaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.39,0:41:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们能想出新的魔术\N{\fs40.9}If we can come up with a new trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.29,0:41:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 再把艺名一改  - 名字不能改\N{\fs40.9}- change the name of the act. - The name stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.36,0:41:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那这个新魔术\N{\fs40.9}Right, well, then the new trick's gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.25,0:41:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得要相当夺人眼球才行\N{\fs40.9}have to be irresistible then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.57,0:41:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有几个办法可以一试\N{\fs40.9}I have a couple of methods to try out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要换一种新的呈现方式\N{\fs40.9}And then we need a new angle on the presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.98,0:41:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想找找灵感\N{\fs40.9}And if you need some inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.88,0:41:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本周在阿尔伯特会堂有个科技展\N{\fs40.9}there's a technical exposition at the Albert Hall this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.11,0:41:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是工程师 科学家那种人去的\N{\fs40.9}Engineers, scientists, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.92,0:41:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西最能引人遐想了\N{\fs40.9}That sort of thing captures the public's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.27,0:41:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意我坐这儿吗 \N{\fs40.9}Mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.40,0:42:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉在狂风暴雨中让我下山来\N{\fs40.9}Tesla sends me down here during the storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.74,0:42:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好借此机会跟"伟大的丹东"喝一杯\N{\fs40.9}Perfect excuse to come join the Great Danton for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.94,0:42:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来两杯酒\N{\fs40.9}Two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.41,0:42:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿真美 老天 我真想念纽约\N{\fs40.9}Beautiful, isn't it? God, I miss New York, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.12,0:42:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那你为什么到这里来  - 这儿闪电集聚\N{\fs40.9}- So, why are you here? - The lightning lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.62,0:42:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没别的了\N{\fs40.9}And not much else.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.32,0:42:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的工作是个秘密\N{\fs40.9}Our work is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.49,0:42:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是密码吗\N{\fs40.9}That a cipher?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.49,0:42:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种循环变换密码 每天的日记都会有变动\N{\fs40.9}It's a rotating transposition that shifts every day of the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.70,0:42:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单 但要完全解开很费时间\N{\fs40.9}Simple but time-consuming to translate,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.83,0:42:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使已经有了那个五个字母的关键词\N{\fs40.9}even with the five-letter keyword.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.77,0:42:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fs40.9}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.57,0:42:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们魔术师有自己的信任圈\N{\fs40.9}We magicians have a circle of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.64,0:42:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟你偷日记的对象还有信任圈可言吗\N{\fs40.9}You have a circle of trust with someone whose diary you stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.81,0:42:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这日记也可以是我买的啊\N{\fs40.9}Maybe I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.64,0:42:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望能在里面找到什么大秘密吗\N{\fs40.9}And you're hoping to find a great secret in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.45,0:42:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经找到了\N{\fs40.9}I've already found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.82,0:42:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才来到这里\N{\fs40.9}That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.42,0:42:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉给另一个魔术师造了一台机器\N{\fs40.9}Tesla built one for another magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么想要一台一模一样的呢\N{\fs40.9}Why would you want the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.96,0:42:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称其为业内竞争吧\N{\fs40.9}Call it a professional rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.03,0:43:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉先生只为不同寻常的人造不同寻常的机器\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Tesla has built unusual machines for unusual people.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.17,0:43:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他从不会在嘴边提起  \N{\fs40.9}But he would never talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.05,0:43:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解他的谨慎\N{\fs40.9}I understand discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.34,0:43:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要那台机器\N{\fs40.9}I just want the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.98,0:43:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把酒喝完\N{\fs40.9}Finish your drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.61,0:43:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你看个东西 \N{\fs40.9}I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.07,0:43:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你会为我们的成就而感到赞叹的\N{\fs40.9}I think you'll have a special appreciation for our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.68,0:43:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你们的工作是个秘密呢  \N{\fs40.9}I thought it was a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.18,0:43:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个魔术师 你说出去也没人信啊\N{\fs40.9}You're a magician. Who's gonna believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.12,0:43:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不久前的成果\N{\fs40.9}Not long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.39,0:43:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的装备需要大笔资金\N{\fs40.9}Our equipment requires a great deal of current.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.93,0:43:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是特斯拉提出 给整个镇供电\N{\fs40.9}Tesla electrified the whole town
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.73,0:43:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来换取我们随时使用发电机的权限\N{\fs40.9}in exchange for using the generators when we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.40,0:43:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在镇上居民睡觉后做实验\N{\fs40.9}We do our tests when the townspeople are asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.48,0:43:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉先生不想吓到别人\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Tesla doesn't want to scare anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.06,0:44:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电线在哪儿呢\N{\fs40.9}Where are the wires?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.44,0:44:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问到点子上了\N{\fs40.9}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.00,0:44:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发电机在哪儿\N{\fs40.9}Where's the generator?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.80,0:44:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上周不是看到过吗\N{\fs40.9}You saw it last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.22,0:44:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那个离这儿至少有十英里吧  - 十五英里\N{\fs40.9}- That must be ten miles from here. - Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.36,0:44:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在回去睡觉前还得把它们都检查一遍呢\N{\fs40.9}And I have to ride all of them before I get to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.56,0:44:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这几天会带信儿给你的 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}I'll send word for you in a few days, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.20,0:44:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术 真正的魔术\N{\fs40.9}Magic. Real magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.42,0:44:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特会堂看到这样的景象\N{\fs40.9}Now appearing, only here at London's Royal Albert Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:35.17,7,,0,0,0,,{\fs62.486\b1\c&H161520&\fnMYoyo PRC Medium\frz7.215\pos(1285.8,431.332)\frx6\fry342}科技奇迹{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:35.17,7,,0,0,0,,{\fnMYoyo PRC Medium\fs62.486\c&H110E16&\frz353.5\pos(579,439.783)\frx6\fry16}科技奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.54,0:44:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们时代的奇迹之一\N{\fs40.9}one of the miracles of our age.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.06,0:44:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科技的瑰宝\N{\fs40.9}A technological marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.38,0:44:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证你前所未见\N{\fs40.9}You've never seen anything like it in your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.70,0:44:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不敢相信自己的眼睛\N{\fs40.9}Your eyes will not believe what they're witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.24,0:44:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是尼古拉·特斯拉创造的奇迹 女士们先生们\N{\fs40.9}The miracle of Nikola Tesla, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.34,0:44:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费 清洁的能源 您想知道未来会是什么样吗 先生\N{\fs40.9}Free, clean power. Would you like to know the future, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.06,0:44:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在讲话的那个人 他将改变世界\N{\fs40.9}The man who's speaking right now is going to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.54,0:44:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 快来吧 赶快坐下 不要犹豫了\N{\fs40.9}Ladies and gentlemen, Come one, come all. Immediate seating, no waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.32,0:44:58.78,3,,0,0,0,,{\frz358.9\c&H3D4849&\fn楷体\fs56.806\b1\3c&H3C474A&\pos(1002,536.343)}交流电奇迹{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.64,0:45:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fs40.9}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.70,0:45:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有听到反对的声音\N{\fs40.9}objections have been raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.86,0:45:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确该反对 你觉得这玩意看上去安全吗\N{\fs40.9}They should be raised. Does that look safe to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.11,0:45:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱迪生的人在给特斯拉先生泼脏水\N{\fs40.9}Part of Thomas Edison's smear campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.06,0:45:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意图阻挡他创造的交流电奇迹\N{\fs40.9}against Mr. Tesla's superior alternating current.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.68,0:45:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经请求特斯拉先生重新考虑\N{\fs40.9}We have asked Mr. Tesla to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.76,0:45:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不会重新考虑呢\N{\fs40.9}Which he will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.99,0:45:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他拒绝在如此不利的情形下出面\N{\fs40.9}But I've been told he refuses to appear under any such restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.23,0:45:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西要爆炸了\N{\fs40.9}This thing's gonna blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.13,0:45:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 别慌张\N{\fs40.9}Ladies and gentlemen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.27,0:46:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs40.9}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.64,0:46:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 杰西\N{\fs40.9}Hello, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.55,0:46:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天跟妈妈玩得开心吗\N{\fs40.9}Have you had a nice day with mommy? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.29,0:46:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\fs40.9}Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.68,0:46:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我爱你  - 看 今天你说的是真心话\N{\fs40.9}- I love you. - See, today it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.18,0:46:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 你好\N{\fs40.9}- Yeah. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.04,0:46:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了幸福\N{\fs40.9}I saw happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.60,0:46:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本该是属于我的幸福\N{\fs40.9}Happiness that should have been mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.84,0:46:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我错了\N{\fs40.9}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.34,0:47:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他的日记本看来 他从未有过我嫉妒的那种生活\N{\fs40.9}His notebook reveals that he never had the life that I envied.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.04,0:47:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这一分钟渴求和美的家庭生活\N{\fs40.9}The family life that he craves one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.62,0:47:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一分钟又弃之敝履 要求自由\N{\fs40.9}he rails against the next, demanding freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.06,0:47:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的思想 他的思想是分裂的\N{\fs40.9}His mind... his mind is a divided one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.04,0:47:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的灵魂浮躁不安\N{\fs40.9}His soul is restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.96,0:47:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的妻子和孩子\N{\fs40.9}His wife and child,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.32,0:47:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被他善变而矛盾的天性所折磨\N{\fs40.9}tormented by his fickle and contradictory nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.00,0:47:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想给她起个什么名字呀\N{\fs40.9}So, what do you think you'll call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.60,0:47:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs40.9}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.12,0:47:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有名字的 她呢\N{\fs40.9}Everybody needs a name, so, what's hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.28,0:47:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫莎拉吧\N{\fs40.9}Maybe Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.32,0:47:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好名字 真是个好名字\N{\fs40.9}That's a lovely name. That's a lovely name.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.90,0:47:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她讲讲你今天打算怎么过吧\N{\fs40.9}Well, you talk about what you want to do for the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.24,0:47:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 说吧 跟她说说\N{\fs40.9}All right, go on, you talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.44,0:47:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要把她带走吗\N{\fs40.9}Are they taking her away?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.78,0:47:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去济贫院吗\N{\fs40.9}To the workhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.33,0:47:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟她说\N{\fs40.9}You keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.76,0:48:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉欧文斯我考虑过了 拿着\N{\fs40.9}Tell Owens I've reconsidered. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.14,0:48:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 拿着\N{\fs40.9}Go on, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.72,0:48:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许是最好的\N{\fs40.9}It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看\N{\fs40.9}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.86,0:48:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要解开"教授"的所有秘密\N{\fs40.9}I'm gonna learn all the professor's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.20,0:48:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先让我教你认字吧\N{\fs40.9}Only if I teach you how to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.38,0:48:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的那些魔术不过是蠢把戏 对不对\N{\fs40.9}They're just stupid tricks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.82,0:48:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们可没法帮你从这儿逃出去\N{\fs40.9}Haven't helped you get out of here, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.36,0:48:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你遇到真的锁还有辙吗 "教授"\N{\fs40.9}Or can't you undo real locks, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.90,0:48:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我只是在消磨时间呢\N{\fs40.9}Or maybe I'm just biding my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.66,0:48:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有一天 我能\N{\fs40.9}Maybe one day I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.12,0:48:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开手上的锁 吸引你的注意\N{\fs40.9}...open my hand, get your attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.90,0:48:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你"你看得足够仔细吗"\N{\fs40.9}ask, "Are you watching closely?"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.88,0:48:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后变一两个魔术\N{\fs40.9}Maybe a magic whirl or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.56,0:48:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再然后 我就从这儿消失了\N{\fs40.9}And then I'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.02,0:48:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么成名的\N{\fs40.9}How'd you get so famous then, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.04,0:48:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术\N{\fs40.9}Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.34,0:49:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 波顿 给我回来\N{\fs40.9}Oi! Borden, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.12,0:49:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fs40.9}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.04,0:49:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴\N{\fs40.9}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.66,0:49:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fs40.9}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.77,0:49:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的钥匙在哪\N{\fs40.9}Where's the bloody key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.48,0:49:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1899年2月8日\N{\fs40.9}February 8, 1899.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.24,0:49:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天终于有了突破\N{\fs40.9}Today, finally, a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉愿意见我了\N{\fs40.9}Tesla's agreed to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.02,0:49:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对安全\N{\fs40.9}Perfectly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.96,0:50:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}So this is the Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.34,0:50:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿利先生把你的事迹全都告诉了我\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Alley has effused about your act to me on any number of occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.94,0:50:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出另一只手\N{\fs40.9}Hold out other hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.08,0:50:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电流的导体是什么  \N{\fs40.9}What's conducting the electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.04,0:50:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身体 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Our bodies, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.94,0:50:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身体能导电 也能发电\N{\fs40.9}Quite capable of conducting and, indeed, producing energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.64,0:50:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃过了吗 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Have you eaten, Mr. Angier?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.74,0:50:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你造一个奇迹\N{\fs40.9}I need something impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.58,0:50:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该对这句话不陌生 "心有余而力不足"\N{\fs40.9}You're familiar with the phrase, "Man's reach exceeds his grasp"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.88,0:50:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是骗人的\N{\fs40.9}Is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.22,0:50:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力是有了 但胆量不够\N{\fs40.9}Man's grasp exceeds his nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.40,0:50:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个社会一次只能容许一个变革的发生\N{\fs40.9}Society only tolerates one change at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.78,0:50:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我第一次尝试改变世界\N{\fs40.9}First time I tried to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.10,0:50:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被当成了空想家\N{\fs40.9}I was hailed as a visionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.38,0:50:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次\N{\fs40.9}Second time...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.56,0:51:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们礼貌地让我退休\N{\fs40.9}...I was asked politely to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.74,0:51:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我现在正在享受退休生活\N{\fs40.9}So here I am, enjoying my retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.44,0:51:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹是存在的 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Nothing is impossible, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过会很昂贵\N{\fs40.9} What you want is simply expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.76,0:51:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我为你造了这台机器\N{\fs40.9}If I were to build for you this machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.98,0:51:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会只把它用于魔术表演吗\N{\fs40.9}you would be presenting it merely as illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.46,0:51:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果人们认为我在舞台上的表演是真的\N{\fs40.9}Well, if people actually believed the things I did on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.86,0:51:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会鼓掌 而是会吓得尖叫的\N{\fs40.9}they wouldn't clap, they'd scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.66,0:51:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想大锯活人吧\N{\fs40.9}Think of sawing a woman in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.40,0:51:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔先生 你想过要这样一台机器得付出什么代价吗\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Angier, Have you considered the cost of such a machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.81,0:51:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱不是问题\N{\fs40.9}Price is not an object.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.81,0:51:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧 但你想过它的代价吗\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps not, but have you considered the cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.75,0:51:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太懂你的意思\N{\fs40.9}I'm not sure I follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.42,0:51:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧 忘了这些\N{\fs40.9}Go home, forget this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.58,0:51:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看出 你已经深深痴迷于此了\N{\fs40.9}I can recognize an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.12,0:51:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有好结果的  \N{\fs40.9}No good will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.80,0:51:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的痴迷没有得到好结果吗\N{\fs40.9}Hasn't good come of your obsessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.26,0:51:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始是这样 但我痴迷的时间太长了\N{\fs40.9}At first, but I have followed them too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.10,0:51:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已沦为它们的奴隶\N{\fs40.9}I am their slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.92,0:51:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早有一天 它们会毁了我\N{\fs40.9}And one day, they will choose to destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.00,0:51:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真懂什么叫痴迷\N{\fs40.9}If you understand an obsession,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.44,0:51:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会知道我心意已决\N{\fs40.9}then you know you won't change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.28,0:52:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺其自然吧\N{\fs40.9}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.80,0:52:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会为我造那台机器吗\N{\fs40.9}Will you build it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.02,0:52:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经开始造了 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}I've already begun to build it, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.66,0:52:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你尽情享受山中的清新空气 你可能得在这儿多待些时日\N{\fs40.9}I hope you enjoy the mountain air. This will take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz3.147\fs68.167\b1\fn微软雅黑\pos(333.6,323.564)\org(435,338)}教\h\h\h\h\h授{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz5.171\fs51.125\fn微软雅黑\b1\pos(360.6,406.663)}超越了死亡{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs45.444\b1\frz4.396\pos(382.8,471.103)}带着全新的魔术华丽回归{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs62.486\b1\frz4.1\pos(390,547.389)}瞬间\h\h\h\h\h\h\h转移{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs45.444\b1\frz5.515\org(600,623)\pos(393.6,598.467)}伦敦城内最精彩纷呈{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.01,0:52:18.89,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs39.764\b1\frz5.372\pos(403.8,662.911)\org(573,702)}为人称道的演出{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.86,0:52:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我以为你已经走了\N{\fs40.9}Uh... I thought you'd gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.40,0:52:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没地方可去\N{\fs40.9}I don't really have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.18,0:52:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都睡在这里吗\N{\fs40.9}You've been sleeping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.24,0:52:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特说我们订到下一个场地前 我可以住在这里 \N{\fs40.9}Cutter said it'd be all right till we get another booking.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.22,0:52:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fs40.9}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.02,0:52:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 调查研究\N{\fs40.9}Uh... research.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.94,0:52:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师的一部分工作\N{\fs40.9}Part of a magician's job
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.58,0:52:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要研究他的对手 看看人家的魔术\N{\fs40.9}is to... watch his competition, see what illusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.56,0:53:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去对那个人做点手脚 对吗\N{\fs40.9}You're going to do something to that man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.17,0:53:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特想让你随他去\N{\fs40.9}Cutter's hoping you let things lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.44,0:53:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 如果波顿认为你俩之间扯平了\N{\fs40.9}He says if Borden thinks things are even between you...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.92,0:53:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯平了\N{\fs40.9}Even?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.18,0:53:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子的命换他的几根手指吗\N{\fs40.9}My wife for a couple of his fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.76,0:53:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在成家了 而且又开始在外面演出了\N{\fs40.9}He has a family now and he's performing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.75,0:53:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿现在过上了他梦寐以求的生活\N{\fs40.9}Borden is out there living his life just as he always intended,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.65,0:53:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个没事人一样 你再看看我\N{\fs40.9}as if nothing had happened and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.42,0:53:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孤身一人 而且没有剧院愿意接纳我\N{\fs40.9}I'm alone and no theater will touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.99,0:53:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们\N{\fs40.9}Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.66,0:53:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要伪装得更好一些\N{\fs40.9}You're going to need a better disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.54,0:53:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一名自愿的观众\N{\fs40.9}I need a volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.81,0:53:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fs40.9}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.52,0:53:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你伤着他了吗\N{\fs40.9}Did you hurt him?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.24,0:53:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}What happened, Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.90,0:53:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 这只是个普通的橡皮球 对吗\N{\fs40.9}You, sir. Just a rubber ball, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.98,0:54:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs40.9}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.14,0:54:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个普通的橡皮球吗 不\N{\fs40.9}Just a rubber ball? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.78,0:54:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它绝不普通 绝不仅仅是个普通的橡皮球\N{\fs40.9}Not normal. Not a normal rubber ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.14,0:54:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔术\N{\fs40.9}It's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.80,0:54:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又有新魔术了\N{\fs40.9}He had a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.04,0:54:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩吗\N{\fs40.9}Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.82,0:54:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我所见过的最精彩的魔术\N{\fs40.9}It was the greatest magic trick I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.60,0:54:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看的时候 底下有人鼓掌吗\N{\fs40.9}Did they applaud when you saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.04,0:54:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔术相当精彩 但也很简单\N{\fs40.9}The trick was too good. It was too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.38,0:54:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众还没反应过来就结束了\N{\fs40.9}The audience hardly had time to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.12,0:54:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是个糟透了的魔术师  \N{\fs40.9}He's a dreadful magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.28,0:54:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他是个天才魔术师\N{\fs40.9}No, he's a wonderful magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.92,0:54:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他是个糟透了的表演者 他不懂怎么去包装节目\N{\fs40.9}He's a dreadful showman. He doesn't know how to dress it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.62,0:54:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 也不知道怎么突出节目的卖点  - 他是怎么做到的\N{\fs40.9}- how to sell it. - How does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.52,0:54:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用替身  \N{\fs40.9}He uses a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.40,0:54:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那太简单了\N{\fs40.9}No, no,no, it's too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.64,0:54:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面肯定有玄机\N{\fs40.9}This is a complex illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.10,0:54:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老这么说 因为你不知道他是怎么弄的\N{\fs40.9}You always say that because you don't know the method.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.42,0:55:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后出来的就是个替身 只能是这么解释\N{\fs40.9}It's a double that comes out. At the end it's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.06,0:55:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过他表演这个魔术三次\N{\fs40.9}I've seen him perform the trick three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.94,0:55:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特先生 最后"拨云见日"的部分还是他本人\N{\fs40.9}And Mr. Cutter, the prestige is the same man.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.86,0:55:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  \N{\fs40.9}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.77,0:55:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证从第二个隔间里出来的就是他本人\N{\fs40.9}The same man comes out of the second cabinet, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.46,0:55:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他本人 \N{\fs40.9}It's the same man.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.02,0:55:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了掩藏他断了的手指 专门戴了衬垫手套\N{\fs40.9}He wears padded gloves to hide his damaged fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.56,0:55:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果看得足够仔细 看得出来的\N{\fs40.9}but, if you look closely, you can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.38,0:55:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不知道怎么去包装节目 但我知道\N{\fs40.9}He doesn't know how to sell his trick to an audience, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.00,0:55:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们可以把它作为整个演出的高潮\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, we could use it as a climax to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.74,0:55:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40.9}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.00,0:55:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他毁了我的人生 我就去偷他的魔术\N{\fs40.9}The man stole my life, I'm gonna steal his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.16,0:55:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得去找个跟你长得像的人\N{\fs40.9}We got to find someone who looks like you on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.28,0:55:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可没用替身  \N{\fs40.9}He doesn't use a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.29,0:55:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特 我不知道波顿是怎么做到的\N{\fs40.9}Robert, I don't know how Borden does his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.89,0:55:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么 你要么等他退休后买他的魔术\N{\fs40.9}Either... You either wait for him to retire and buy the secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.46,0:55:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么就认真听我的方法\N{\fs40.9}or you listen to how I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.33,0:55:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的唯一方法\N{\fs40.9}And the only way that I know how to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.93,0:55:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去给你找个替身\N{\fs40.9}is to find you a bloody good double.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.40,0:55:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40.9}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.52,0:55:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看仔细了 我们出去找我的替身吧\N{\fs40.9}Take a good look. Let's get out there and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.01,0:55:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了 \N{\fs40.9}Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.05,0:56:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs40.9}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.92,0:56:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的  \N{\fs40.9}It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.16,0:56:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs40.9}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.85,0:56:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs40.9}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.83,0:56:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fs40.9}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.66,0:56:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我上星期问你 你说  - 我当时心情不好\N{\fs40.9}- I asked you last week, you said... - You caught me in a wrong mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但你怎么会  - 莎拉\N{\fs40.9}- But you won't ever... - Sarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.22,0:56:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法是会改变的\N{\fs40.9}I'm gonna have to change my mind, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.27,0:56:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的演出正如火如荼 \N{\fs40.9}The act is taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.88,0:56:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快我们就能在更大的剧院演出了 前景一片大好\N{\fs40.9}Soon we'll be in a bigger theater, things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.76,0:56:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信 谢谢你 谢谢你 真漂亮\N{\fs40.9}I can't believe it. Thank you. Thank you. It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.30,0:56:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 格里  - 亲爱的 你真美\N{\fs40.9}- Gerry? - Darling, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.54,0:56:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特先生 安吉尔先生 来认识一下杰拉尔德·鲁特\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Cutter, Mr. Angier, I'd like you to meet Gerald Root.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.94,0:56:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣幸之至 认识你们两位绅士真是荣幸之至\N{\fs40.9}A pleasure. Pleasure to meet you fine gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.38,0:57:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听我讲个笑话吗 过来\N{\fs40.9}Would you like for me to tell you a little joke? Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.24,0:57:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 你笑了吗\N{\fs40.9}Yes. Are you laughing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.48,0:57:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去尿个尿\N{\fs40.9}I have to take a piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.98,0:57:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他简直神经病  \N{\fs40.9}He's out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.08,0:57:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 他是个过气演员\N{\fs40.9}Of course, he's an out-of-work actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.12,0:57:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他了 他还需要捯饬一下\N{\fs40.9}He's perfect. He needs a little help.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.76,0:57:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完事后 我可以让你俩看起来就像两兄弟 \N{\fs40.9}But when I get done with him, he could be your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.78,0:57:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要他看起来像我兄弟 我要他跟我一模一样\N{\fs40.9}I don't need him to be my brother, I need him to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.68,0:57:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一个月的时间\N{\fs40.9}Give me a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.84,0:57:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打开这扇门\N{\fs40.9}So you open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.90,0:57:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后\N{\fs40.9}...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.66,0:57:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来呀\N{\fs40.9}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.18,0:57:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能找个更软的垫子吗\N{\fs40.9}Couldn't you have found a softer one?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.74,0:57:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正又不是要在上面睡觉\N{\fs40.9}Well, it's not for sleeping on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.44,0:57:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你从那儿掉下来\N{\fs40.9}So, if you come down through there...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.22,0:58:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 然后鲁特从那边升上去吗  - 没错\N{\fs40.9}- ...does Root go up through there? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.62,0:58:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众一定会叫好的\N{\fs40.9}It's going to be amazing, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.86,0:58:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定的 \N{\fs40.9}Well, it has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.10,0:58:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿的魔术人气越来越高了\N{\fs40.9}Borden's trick is getting noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.54,0:58:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他的场子又坐满了\N{\fs40.9}The place was packed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.82,0:58:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又去看他的演出了\N{\fs40.9}You went and saw his show again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.58,0:58:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好见你的替身了吗 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Ready to meet yourself, Mr. Angier?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.78,0:58:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要让自己看起来烂醉如泥\N{\fs40.9}All I have to do is keep myself stinking drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.92,0:58:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没人能看出我俩的区别了\N{\fs40.9}and no one will be able to tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.22,0:58:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点信心嘛 先生\N{\fs40.9}Have a little faith, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.44,0:58:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能表演给我们看看吗 鲁特先生\N{\fs40.9}Now, would you favor us with a performance, Mr. Root?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.90,0:59:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你对这个世界的认识有我的一半多 你也会去天天买醉的\N{\fs40.9}You'd drink, too, if you knew the world half as well as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.84,0:59:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你很特别吗 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Did you think you were unique, Mr. Angier?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.56,0:59:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我演过凯撒 还演过浮士德\N{\fs40.9}I've been Caesar, I've played Faust.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.40,0:59:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演个"伟大的丹东"有多难\N{\fs40.9}How difficult could it possibly be to play the Great Danton?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.54,0:59:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以回去做你自己 鲁特 不过没钱赚\N{\fs40.9}You can go back to being yourself now, Root, for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.02,0:59:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我宁愿演他\N{\fs40.9}I'd rather be him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.22,0:59:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是挺有趣的\N{\fs40.9}I find it, uh... amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.32,0:59:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"陛下\N{\fs40.9}"My liege,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.08,0:59:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有拒交战俘"\N{\fs40.9}I did deny no prisoners."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.32,0:59:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22.723}莎士比亚<亨利四世>中台词
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.36,0:59:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去好极了  \N{\fs40.9}You look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.80,0:59:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs40.9}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.68,0:59:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁特要保持低调 要是有人看见他 我们就玩完了\N{\fs40.9}Root has to keep a low profile. Anyone sees him, the game's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.93,0:59:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么做到的 卡特 \N{\fs40.9}I don't know how you do things, Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.80,0:59:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也不想知道\N{\fs40.9}I'm not sure I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.36,0:59:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有想过我们该给这魔术起个什么名字\N{\fs40.9}Have you thought what we should call the trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.38,0:59:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不必拐弯抹角\N{\fs40.9}There's no point being coy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.81,0:59:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然波顿的魔术叫"瞬间转移"\N{\fs40.9}Borden calls his trick The Transported Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.42,0:59:50.75,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs79.527\b1\c&H304354&\pos(935.4,165.698)}新瞬间转移{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.28,0:59:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 到现在为止 今晚您看到的 \N{\fs40.9}Ladies and gentlemen, much of what you've seen
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.52,0:59:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许都是些平常魔术 小把戏\N{\fs40.9}may be termed as illusions or entertaining trifles.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.95,1:00:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs40.9}Alas...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.19,1:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来这个节目可非同一般\N{\fs40.9}...I cannot claim this next feat as illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.63,1:00:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看仔细了\N{\fs40.9}Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.26,1:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会在魔术里看到任何诡计\N{\fs40.9}You will see no trickery,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.77,1:00:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个魔术本身就不含有诡计\N{\fs40.9}for no trickery is employed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.94,1:00:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是古老东方的人们 以及喜马拉雅山上的圣贤们\N{\fs40.9}Merely a technique familiar to certain citizens of the Orient
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.37,1:00:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所熟悉的一种技法\N{\fs40.9}and various holy men of the Himalayas.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.81,1:00:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你们当中也有许多人对这种技法有所了解\N{\fs40.9}Indeed, many of you may be familiar with this technique,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.91,1:00:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不了解的人也别紧张\N{\fs40.9}but for those of you who are not, do not be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.15,1:00:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证 接下来你所看到的东西绝对安全\N{\fs40.9}What you're about to see is considered safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.79,1:01:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我们的成功干杯\N{\fs40.9}To our achievement.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.92,1:01:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧院经理说他从未看到过观众反响那么热烈\N{\fs40.9}The manager says he's never seen a reaction like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.87,1:01:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他还能看到观众的反应 \N{\fs40.9}At least he got to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.52,1:01:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在大家喝彩时只能躲在台下\N{\fs40.9}I spent the ovation hiding under the stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.24,1:01:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在意那个消失的人 那个掉落台下的人\N{\fs40.9}No one cares about the man who disappears, the man who goes into\Nthe box.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.65,1:01:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们只会在意那个从另一边出来的人\N{\fs40.9}They care about the one who comes out the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.72,1:01:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在意那个躲在台下的人\N{\fs40.9}I care about the man in the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.85,1:01:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 要不这样吧 我们两个可以换换角色\N{\fs40.9}Thank you. I don't know, maybe we could switch before the trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.22,1:01:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做"拨云见日"的部分 让鲁特在台下呆着\N{\fs40.9}That way I could be the Prestige and Root ends up below stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.46,1:01:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 魔术前的营造声势是最重要的环节\N{\fs40.9}No, the anticipation of the trick is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.46,1:01:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你的口才来制造悬念\N{\fs40.9}We need your showmanship to build up the suspense.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.60,1:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁特要是开口\N{\fs40.9}Once Root opens his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.98,1:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就全完了 他可胜任不了这工作\N{\fs40.9}it's over. He can't introduce this trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.23,1:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不能的 我可是"伟大的丹东"\N{\fs40.9}Of course I can. I'm the Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.04,1:01:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁特 你这该死的蠢材 快把这身行头换掉\N{\fs40.9}Root, you bloody fool, get out of that wardrobe and makeup.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.71,1:01:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里随时可能有外人进来\N{\fs40.9}Anyone could walk in here at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.44,1:01:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜大家了\N{\fs40.9}Congratulations, all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.58,1:01:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的景象可不是每天都能见到的 罗比我们为此付出了这么多\N{\fs40.9}Life is not full of these moments, Robbie. We worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.35,1:01:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理应好好庆祝一下\N{\fs40.9}We need to celebrate properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.75,1:02:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 又想起你的妻子了吗\N{\fs40.9}What's wrong? Is it your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.29,1:02:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是这个魔术 它还不够好\N{\fs40.9}No, it's the trick. It isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.66,1:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿的魔术可没法跟我们的比 他一点派头都没有\N{\fs40.9}Borden's trick is nothing compared to ours. He has no style.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.06,1:02:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他可不用在谢幕时躲在台下\N{\fs40.9}He doesn't spend the finale hiding under the stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.00,1:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我得知道他是怎么做的  - 为什么\N{\fs40.9}- I need to know how he does it. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.97,1:02:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做得比他更好\N{\fs40.9}So I can do it better.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.76,1:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你去为他工作\N{\fs40.9}I need you to go and work for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.28,1:02:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为他工作 你是认真的吗\N{\fs40.9}Work for him? Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.20,1:02:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当我的间谍吧\N{\fs40.9}You'll be my spy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.50,1:02:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的演出刚有起色 现在你却让我走\N{\fs40.9}We just got our start. Now you want me to leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.66,1:02:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们才能先人一步嘛 想想看 奥利维娅\N{\fs40.9}That's how we advance. Think of it, Olivia...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.75,1:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特版本的"瞬间转移"已经吸引了很多观众 \N{\fs40.9}we've got people excited about Cutter's version of the trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.90,1:02:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想当我们知道了这个魔术的真正秘诀 会是什么样子\N{\fs40.9}Imagine what we'd do with the real illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.04,1:02:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能演出前无古人的精彩魔术\N{\fs40.9}We'd have the greatest magic act anyone's ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.70,1:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道我为你做事  \N{\fs40.9}He knows I work for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.34,1:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此 他才会雇用你\N{\fs40.9}Exactly why he'll want to hire you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.52,1:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想知道我的秘密  \N{\fs40.9}He'll want my secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.66,1:02:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他凭什么相信我\N{\fs40.9}Why would he trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.00,1:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你会把真相告诉他\N{\fs40.9}Because you're gonna tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.84,1:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs40.9}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.12,1:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好女孩儿\N{\fs40.9}Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.48,1:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很好奇 自己的钱都被花到什么地方去了吧\N{\fs40.9}You must be curious to see what so much money has bought you, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.62,1:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该让你来看看它首次使用的情况\N{\fs40.9}Fitting you should be here for her maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.58,1:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把你的帽子给我\N{\fs40.9}Your hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.24,1:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您最好退后点\N{\fs40.9}You might want to stand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.54,1:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs40.9}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.62,1:03:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不您先让我们自己处理一下吧\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps it would be best if you left us to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.14,1:03:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么问题吗 特斯拉先生\N{\fs40.9}Is there a problem, Mr. Tesla?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.60,1:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没事 下周再来吧  - 下周\N{\fs40.9}- No. Come back next week. - Next week?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.80,1:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 下周就好了  - 特斯拉\N{\fs40.9}- Next week, it will be fine. - Tesla!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.34,1:04:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器只是有点不稳定\N{\fs40.9}Just a little temperamental.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.91,1:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作坊不错  \N{\fs40.9}Interesting workshop.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.06,1:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 凑合吧\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, we make do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.06,1:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的名字叫奥利维娅  - 我知道你是谁\N{\fs40.9}- My name is Olivia... - I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.46,1:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这儿偷我的戏法吗\N{\fs40.9}Here to steal the rest of my show?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.94,1:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是来帮你弥补演出的不足\N{\fs40.9}No. I'm here to give your show what is missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.00,1:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 不足的是什么呢  \N{\fs40.9}Yeah, what might that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.28,1:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs40.9}Me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.74,1:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚不还在说吗 伯纳德\N{\fs40.9}Wasn't I just saying that, right, Bernard?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.74,1:04:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女性的魅力  \N{\fs40.9}A woman's touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.00,1:04:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开了 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}I've left Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.32,1:04:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我需要一份工作\N{\fs40.9}- All right. - I want a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.17,1:04:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs40.9}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.57,1:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你没理由相信我\N{\fs40.9}I know you've no reason to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.14,1:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会不相信你呢\N{\fs40.9}Why wouldn't I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.11,1:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过是我的仇敌的情妇罢了 我怎么会不相信你呢\N{\fs40.9}I mean, you're only the mistress of my enemy. Why wouldn't I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.46,1:04:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 波顿先生  - 叫我阿尔弗雷德\N{\fs40.9}- Mr. Borden. - Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.58,1:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把真相告诉你\N{\fs40.9}I'm going to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.32,1:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只不过是我们这一行用来耍滑头的障眼法 \N{\fs40.9}Now that is a slippery notion in our line of work,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.94,1:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 温小姐\N{\fs40.9}isn't it, Miss Wenscombe?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.26,1:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他派我到这儿来的\N{\fs40.9}I am here because he sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.94,1:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想让我为你做事 窃取你的秘密\N{\fs40.9}He wants me to come and work for you and steal your secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.64,1:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要我的秘密干嘛呢 他的魔术都首屈一指了\N{\fs40.9}What does he need my secret for? His trick is topnotch.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.28,1:05:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这边消失 然后再飞快地在舞台的另一端出现 \N{\fs40.9}He vanishes, and then he reappears instantly
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.60,1:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这一瞬间的功夫他变得沉默无声了 变胖了\N{\fs40.9}on the other side of the stage, mute, overweight
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.20,1:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还添了几分酒气\N{\fs40.9}and, unless I'm mistaken, very drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.64,1:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太令人震惊了 他是怎么做到的 \N{\fs40.9}It's astonishing. How does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.92,1:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有告诉我 奥利维娅\N{\fs40.9}And, and tell me, Olivia,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.90,1:05:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他享受呆在台下向观众鞠躬致意吗\N{\fs40.9}does he enjoy taking his bows under the stage?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.86,1:05:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这简直让他抓狂 他现在着了魔地要知道你的秘诀\N{\fs40.9}No. It's killing him. He's obsessed with discovering your methods.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.30,1:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的什么事都不在乎了 对我们的成功也开心不起来\N{\fs40.9}He thinks of nothing else. He takes no pleasure in our success.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.88,1:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了\N{\fs40.9}And I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.02,1:05:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着他没有未来\N{\fs40.9}There is no future with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.36,1:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他派我来窃取你的秘密\N{\fs40.9}He sent me here to steal your secrets,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.34,1:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实我要来把他的秘密告诉你\N{\fs40.9}but I've actually come to offer you his.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.56,1:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真相 对吗\N{\fs40.9}This is the truth... is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.70,1:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好赶紧装扮好 先生\N{\fs40.9}Think you'd better get dressed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.68,1:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁特 你迟到了 而且喝得比平时还要醉\N{\fs40.9}Root, you're late and more drunk than usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.06,1:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上去升降梯下候场\N{\fs40.9}Get down below stairs right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.30,1:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40.9}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.12,1:05:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们有必要好好聊一聊 卡特先生\N{\fs40.9}No, we need to have a little chat, Mr. Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.54,1:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了 卡特\N{\fs40.9}We have a problem. Cutter,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.18,1:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波顿的演出搬到我们街对面来了\N{\fs40.9}Borden is performing right across the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.34,1:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我们还有个更大的麻烦\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, we have a bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.12,1:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲁特 他意识到自己可以狮子大开口了\N{\fs40.9}Root. He's realized that he can make demands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.90,1:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 他在敲诈我们吗\N{\fs40.9}Wha...? He's blackmailing us?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.44,1:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺惊讶的 说实话\N{\fs40.9}I was surprised, to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.88,1:06:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说 这些人要用更长的时间才能反应过来他们的价值\N{\fs40.9}It usually takes them a lot longer to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.72,1:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要多少钱  \N{\fs40.9}How much does he want?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.90,1:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱多钱少不是关键\N{\fs40.9}It makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.64,1:06:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须马上停止表演这个魔术\N{\fs40.9}We've got to stop doing the trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.02,1:06:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止表演这个魔术 卡特 看看这个\N{\fs40.9}Stop the trick? Cutter, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.42,1:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,818)}看看昨天和上周的报纸 \N{\fs40.9}Look at yesterday's. And last week's,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:14.64,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.72\clip()\fn宋体\fs51.125\b1\c&H23292A&\fscx85\fscy81\pos(931.8,219.371)}班狄斯剧院{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:14.64,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.53\fn宋体\fs34.083\b1\pos(941.4,252.032)}下周起{\b1}为您呈现{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:14.64,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz10.63\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs62.486\c&H1A2122&\pos(984,329.598)\fscx123\fscy83}教\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h授
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:14.64,5,,0,0,0,,{\frz9.165\fs62.486\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fscx155\fscy87\pos(1016.4,422.583)\org(1019,461)}原版瞬间转移
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.70,1:06:14.64,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs34.083\c&H191D1F&\b1\frz19.67\fscx163\fscy111\pos(1120.8,614.409)}我们拒绝接受廉价的模仿
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.22,1:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说你是"伦敦最顶尖的舞台表演者"\N{\fs40.9}where they said you were the "premier stage performer in London".
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.08,1:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是"魔术师" 注意了 你在他们眼里只是个表演者\N{\fs40.9}Not "magician", mind you. Performer of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.52,1:06:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么  \N{\fs40.9}What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.52,1:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说 罗伯特 你现在爬得太高\N{\fs40.9}My point is, Robert, you've climbed too high
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.14,1:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致你找不准自己的职业定位了\N{\fs40.9}to get away with professional embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.84,1:06:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要表演任何不在我们能力范围内的魔术\N{\fs40.9}We don't do any tricks we can't control.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.08,1:06:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要多少钱 先给他 \N{\fs40.9}Just pay him whatever he wants for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.40,1:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先继续表演这个魔术 等波顿那边开始了\N{\fs40.9}We keep doing the trick until Borden opens,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.34,1:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再慢慢淡出\N{\fs40.9}and then we'll phase it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.10,1:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40.9}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.62,1:06:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁特无故变坏 这让卡特感到惊讶\N{\fs40.9}Cutter was always surprised how fast Root turned bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.06,1:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有人盛情赠我一品脱啤酒 我就没必要推辞了\N{\fs40.9}To what do I owe the pleasure of this rather welcome pint of ale?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.18,1:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你是"伟大的丹东" 对吧  - 嘘 别招摇\N{\fs40.9}- You're the Great Danton, aren't you? - Sh, sh, sh, sh, sh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.62,1:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我 但我很低调\N{\fs40.9}Of course I am, but don't advertise it,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.46,1:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的仰慕者都太疯狂了\N{\fs40.9}because I'll be mobbed with fans.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.42,1:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给他的钱足够他去花天酒地\N{\fs40.9}We paid him enough to keep him in beers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.36,1:07:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没理由从中作梗\N{\fs40.9}You wouldn't expect him to rock the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.84,1:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你们当中也有许多人对这种技法有所了解\N{\fs40.9}Many of you may be familiar with this technique,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.46,1:07:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不了解的人也别紧张\N{\fs40.9}but for those of you who aren't, do not be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.14,1:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证 接下来你所看到的东西绝对安全\N{\fs40.9}What you're about to see is considered safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.54,1:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是谁  \N{\fs40.9}And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.88,1:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的一个仰慕者 跟你是同行\N{\fs40.9}I am a humble admirer and a fellow practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.80,1:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很好\N{\fs40.9}Mmm. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.28,1:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一杯  \N{\fs40.9}Another one?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.24,1:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 恭敬不如从命了\N{\fs40.9}Oh, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.80,1:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚不表演\N{\fs40.9}I'm not performing tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.30,1:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一天只演一场 但实话说\N{\fs40.9}I'm only doing one show, but to be frank,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.80,1:07:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在基本是我的手下再帮我打理事情了\N{\fs40.9}my people pretty much run things these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.86,1:07:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上去 \N{\fs40.9}Get up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.58,1:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上去\N{\fs40.9}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.52,1:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的魔术 "瞬间转移"\N{\fs40.9}Your illusion, The Transported Man,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.72,1:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想窃取你这个魔术的秘密\N{\fs40.9}I'm not claiming to know your methods,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.54,1:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我以前也表演过跟这相似的一个魔术\N{\fs40.9}but I had a similar trick in my act,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.08,1:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我用了个替身\N{\fs40.9}and, uh... I used a double.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.28,1:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白 很聪明  \N{\fs40.9}Mm, I see, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.56,1:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始很顺利 但后来情况就急转直下了\N{\fs40.9}Well, it was, and then it went bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.25,1:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我万万没想到 \N{\fs40.9}What I didn't count on was that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.98,1:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在魔术里用的那个替身\N{\fs40.9}when I incorporated this bloke into my act,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.10,1:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他完全掌握了主动权\N{\fs40.9}he had complete power over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.24,1:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说主动权吗\N{\fs40.9}Complete power, you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.72,1:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs40.9}Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.15,1:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要当心 别让别人拥有了主动权 凌驾于你\N{\fs40.9}Be very careful giving someone that power over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.48,1:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs40.9}Huh. Thank you. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.89,1:08:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的忠告\N{\fs40.9}Yes, thank you for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.16,1:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 干杯\N{\fs40.9}Hmm. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.96,1:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来这个节目可非同一般\N{\fs40.9}I cannot claim this next feat as illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.36,1:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你所看到的东西绝对安全\N{\fs40.9}What you're about to see is considered safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.14,1:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs40.9}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.94,1:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这不是"伟大的丹东"吗\N{\fs40.9}Oh! The Great Danton.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.13,1:09:41.34,白色无边,,0,0,0,,{\fn钟齐吴嘉睿手写字\fs68.167\b0\frz13.02\pos(967.999,470.283)}班狄斯剧院开场演出{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.13,1:09:41.34,白色无边,,0,0,0,,{\fs68.167\b0\fn钟齐吴嘉睿手写字\frz7.339\pos(1030.001,712.72)}教授{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.95,1:09:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此表示抱歉\N{\fs40.9}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.89,1:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街对面班狄斯剧院的魔术表演要精彩得多\N{\fs40.9}There simply is too much magic... for my stage at The Pantages across the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.96,1:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我的冒昧\N{\fs40.9}Pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.98,1:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 别对那可怜小伙太苛刻了 他也的确尽力了\N{\fs40.9}And go easy on the poor chap. He does try so very hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.36,1:10:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道波顿是怎么找到他的\N{\fs40.9}I don't know how Borden found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.55,1:10:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直小心翼翼地把他藏着\N{\fs40.9}Kept him under wraps. I was careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.52,1:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他还是找到了\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, well, he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.35,1:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得会是她说的吗\N{\fs40.9}Do you think it was her?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.96,1:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道我要来吗\N{\fs40.9}You weren't expecting me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.63,1:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你会更早来 你之前说的是下午\N{\fs40.9}I was expecting you sooner. Your message said afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.30,1:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我行动可有点不便\N{\fs40.9}Well, it takes a bit for me to get around these days...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.12,1:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把我的一切都夺走了 我的妻子 我的事业\N{\fs40.9}He's taken everything from me. My wife, my career,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.18,1:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还夺走了你  \N{\fs40.9}now you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.98,1:10:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思 明明是你派我过去的\N{\fs40.9}What do you mean? You sent me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.84,1:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派你去窃取他的秘密 不是去给他的表演增色\N{\fs40.9}I sent you to steal his secret, not to improve his act.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.98,1:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的工作  \N{\fs40.9}It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.84,1:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不是爱上他\N{\fs40.9}Or to fall in love with him!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.54,1:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你让我做的我可都做了  - 是吗 是吗\N{\fs40.9}- I did everything you asked! - Yes? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.45,1:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那魔术是怎么变的  \N{\fs40.9}How does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.53,1:10:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟卡特说的一样 用替身\N{\fs40.9}Cutter was right- it's a double.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.94,1:10:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当然会这样告诉你  \N{\fs40.9}'Course he said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.40,1:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么都没说\N{\fs40.9}He didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.32,1:10:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己看到的 化妆用品\N{\fs40.9}I've seen things, makeup,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.62,1:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜 假发 都是我们演出的时候不会用到的东西\N{\fs40.9}glasses, wigs. We don't use any of it for the show,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.84,1:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这些我都在后台看到了 \N{\fs40.9}but I've seen it hidden backstage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.47,1:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是为了误导你 他故意把这些东西到处放 \N{\fs40.9}It's misdirection, he leaves those things lying around
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.98,1:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是要让你以为他在用替身\N{\fs40.9}to make you think he's using a double.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.40,1:11:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这样吗 他又不知道我什么时候会去看\N{\fs40.9}All the time? He doesn't know when I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.33,1:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是一直这样 奥利维娅 他就是这样的人\N{\fs40.9}All the time, Olivia! That's who he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.63,1:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了魔术表演就必须得这样\N{\fs40.9}That's what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.97,1:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人生就是一场表演 你还没看出来吗\N{\fs40.9}He lives his act, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.44,1:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他上床 并不意味着他就信任你了\N{\fs40.9}Just because you're sleeping with him doesn't mean he trusts you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.88,1:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得自己对任何事都了如指掌 对吧\N{\fs40.9}You think you can see everything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.35,1:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"伟大的丹东"才是个盲目的傻瓜\N{\fs40.9}The Great Danton is a blind fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.25,1:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的日记本\N{\fs40.9}His notebook.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.02,1:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷来的\N{\fs40.9}You stole it?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.52,1:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借的 就一个晚上\N{\fs40.9}I borrowed it for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.44,1:11:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你应该能解开其中一部分\N{\fs40.9}I thought you could translate some of it...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.26,1:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到 奥利维娅 没人能做到 这全是密码\N{\fs40.9}I can't. Olivia, no one can. It's a cipher.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.63,1:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有解密的关键词 也得花上好几个月才能全部解开\N{\fs40.9}Even with the keyword, it will take months to decode.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.13,1:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有关键词呢  \N{\fs40.9}And without the keyword?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.72,1:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许永远解不开了\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps never.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.10,1:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说吧  \N{\fs40.9}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.98,1:11:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有再说\N{\fs40.9}We will not see.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.80,1:11:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我明早前没有把日记本放回原处 \N{\fs40.9}If I don't get that back till by tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.65,1:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就会知道是我拿的了\N{\fs40.9}he'll know I took it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.81,1:11:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开他吧  \N{\fs40.9}Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.73,1:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他知道我住哪儿\N{\fs40.9}I can't. He knows where I live.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.44,1:11:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是他的日记 奥利维娅\N{\fs40.9}This is his diary, Olivia.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.18,1:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所有的秘密都牢牢抓在我的手里了\N{\fs40.9}All of his secrets are right here in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.92,1:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这无法让你的妻子起死回生\N{\fs40.9}It won't bring your wife back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.58,1:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管我妻子 我只关心他的秘密\N{\fs40.9}I don't care about my wife. I care about his secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.53,1:12:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我\N{\fs40.9}Look, I'll, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.74,1:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去他的工作坊 弄成有人非法闯入的样子\N{\fs40.9}I'll go to his workshop and stage a break-in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.74,1:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会知道是你拿了的  \N{\fs40.9}He'll know you took it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.55,1:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是我 不是你\N{\fs40.9}Yes, me. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.04,1:12:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗\N{\fs40.9}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.84,1:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.18,1:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经爱上他了\N{\fs40.9}I have fallen in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.78,1:12:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那让你这么做可真是难为你了\N{\fs40.9}Then I know how hard this has been for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.82,1:12:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记本不见了吗\N{\fs40.9}Notebook?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.98,1:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他才刚刚开始\N{\fs40.9}I think he's just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.21,1:13:01.25,6,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry306\fn微软雅黑\fs68.167\c&HC5AAB1&\fscx107\fscy173\b1\pos(606,473.423)}班\N狄\N斯{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.21,1:13:01.25,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs56.806\c&H040203&\frx16\fry28\frz345.5\pos(961.8,423.522)\org(992,358)}教授
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.21,1:13:01.25,4,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs45.444\c&H040203&\fscx92\fscy136\frx20\fry22\frz351\pos(1008,537.722)}原版瞬间转移
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.32,1:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"教授"\N{\fs40.9}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.68,1:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\fs40.9}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.06,1:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚想在街上走走\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, I'm walking tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.44,1:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要来就来吧 我不在乎\N{\fs40.9}Let him come. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.70,1:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"教授" "教授"\N{\fs40.9}Professor! Professor!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.06,1:15:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs40.9}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.00,1:15:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗  \N{\fs40.9}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.18,1:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死不了\N{\fs40.9}I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.56,1:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省得我给你钻个出气孔了\N{\fs40.9}Saves me cutting you an air hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.82,1:15:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 真是了不起啊  - 为什么\N{\fs40.9}- I'm impressed. - Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.58,1:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于让自己弄脏手了\N{\fs40.9}You're finally getting your hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.52,1:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好魔术就得付出这样的代价 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}It's what a good trick costs, Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.50,1:15:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险 牺牲\N{\fs40.9}Risk, sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.82,1:15:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这牺牲恐怕会是你的吧\N{\fs40.9}The sacrifice, I'm afraid, is all gonna be yours,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.00,1:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你把我想要的东西给我\N{\fs40.9}unless you give me what I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.90,1:15:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要什么  \N{\fs40.9}Which is?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.92,1:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的秘密\N{\fs40.9}Your secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.42,1:15:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的秘密\N{\fs40.9}My secret?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.24,1:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"瞬间转移"魔术的秘诀是什么\N{\fs40.9}Your method for The Transported Man.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.84,1:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法隆不肯告诉我 他好像不太爱说话\N{\fs40.9}Fallon wouldn't tell me. In fact, he doesn't seem to talk at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.72,1:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都有我的日记本了  \N{\fs40.9}You have my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.04,1:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关键词 那一文不值\N{\fs40.9}Useless without the keyword.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.70,1:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的秘诀写下来 波顿先生 要从头到尾清清楚楚\N{\fs40.9}Write down your method, Mr. Borden, describe it in full.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.14,1:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你的整个秘诀 不是关键词\N{\fs40.9}I want the whole method, not the keyword.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.20,1:16:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道你有没有把它写在日记本里\N{\fs40.9}I don't know if your secret's in your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.56,1:16:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键词就是秘诀\N{\fs40.9}The keyword is the method.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.52,1:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的道具师呢\N{\fs40.9}Where's my ingenieur?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.96,1:16:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着吗  \N{\fs40.9}Alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.44,1:16:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你挖得多快了\N{\fs40.9}How fast can you dig?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.06,1:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法隆 听得到吗 法隆\N{\fs40.9}Fallon, you hear me? Fallon!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.70,1:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胳膊怎么样了  \N{\fs40.9}How's the arm?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.07,1:16:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还吊着呢\N{\fs40.9}Still attached.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.82,1:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你的答案了吗\N{\fs40.9}Did you find your answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.28,1:16:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的答案 卡特 我还没打开看呢\N{\fs40.9}Our answer, Cutter. I haven't looked yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.70,1:16:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起分享\N{\fs40.9}I wanted you to share this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.98,1:16:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道他是怎么做的了 罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}I already know how he does it, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.62,1:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟他一贯的做法一样 就跟我们的做法一样\N{\fs40.9}Same way he always has, the same way as we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.65,1:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过你觉得不只这些罢了\N{\fs40.9}It's just that you want something more.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.19,1:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们来揭晓答案吧\N{\fs40.9}Well, let's find out then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.48,1:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs40.9}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.79,1:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs43.173}即 尼古拉·特斯拉 交流电发明者
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.54,1:17:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是 卡特 我们要踏上旅途了\N{\fs40.9}It means, Cutter, we have a journey ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.07,1:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去美国  -罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}- To America. - Robert?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.01,1:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fs40.9}Listen, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.05,1:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痴迷是年轻人的游戏\N{\fs40.9}Obsession is a young man's game.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.96,1:17:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fs40.9}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.42,1:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法再陪你继续前行了\N{\fs40.9}I can't follow you any further in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.72,1:17:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到了 对不起\N{\fs40.9}I can't, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.10,1:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来就由我一个人完成吧\N{\fs40.9}Then the rest is up to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.53,1:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.37,1:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 你好啊 亲爱的\N{\fs40.9}Good evening. Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.30,1:17:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上你们最好的香槟\N{\fs40.9}Champagne, your finest.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.54,1:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我们的晚餐还有客人\N{\fs40.9}I didn't know we were going to be joined for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.02,1:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我们要庆祝嘛\N{\fs40.9}Absolutely, we are celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.76,1:18:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温小姐 法隆先生\N{\fs40.9}Miss Wenscombe, Mr. Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.58,1:18:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要庆祝什么  \N{\fs40.9}Well, what are we celebrating?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.12,1:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又有新魔术了\N{\fs40.9}Well, we've hit upon a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.68,1:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对吧  - 什么魔术 Freddie\N{\fs40.9}- Haven't we? - What trick, Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.52,1:18:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 弗雷迪 什么魔术\N{\fs40.9}Yes, Freddie, what trick?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.62,1:18:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天晚上把自己活埋\N{\fs40.9}I am going to bury myself alive every night,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.10,1:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有人会来把我挖出来 好极了\N{\fs40.9}and then someone will come along and dig me up. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.03,1:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想我丈夫喝醉了  - 没有 继续倒香槟\N{\fs40.9}- I think my husband's had quite enough... - No, pour the champagne.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.06,1:18:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 倒  \N{\fs40.9}Come on, pour the...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.54,1:18:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 别那样对我说话 我又不是个小屁孩\N{\fs40.9}Sarah, don't talk to me like that. I'm not a bloody child.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.97,1:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要不我们  - 要不 法隆先生 \N{\fs40.9}- Perhaps it would be better... - Perhaps, Mr. Fallon,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.82,1:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你送温小姐回家吧\N{\fs40.9}you might escort Miss Wenscombe home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.24,1:18:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我丈夫胡言乱语  - 拜托\N{\fs40.9}- My husband's being a bore. - Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.15,1:18:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们没必要在这儿跟着受罪  - 别毁了这个夜晚\N{\fs40.9}- I see no reason you should suffer. - Don't ruin this evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.62,1:18:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 波顿夫人 晚安 弗雷迪\N{\fs40.9}Good night, Mrs. Borden. Good night, Freddie.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.06,1:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 弗雷迪  - 那是我的名字啊\N{\fs40.9}- Freddie? - Well that's my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.26,1:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 家里没人这么叫你  - 我又不是每时每刻都在家 对吧\N{\fs40.9}- Not at home. - I'm not always at home, am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.42,1:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你至少先把脸上的胡子取下来吧\N{\fs40.9}Couldn't you have at least taken off the, the beard?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.54,1:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 我刚刚从那个该死的剧院出来\N{\fs40.9}Sarah, I just came from the bloody theater just now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.40,1:19:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 我现在在公共场合 \N{\fs40.9}All right? I'm out in public.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.14,1:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都乐意看到我这样的形象\N{\fs40.9}Everybody else loves it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.46,1:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这个样子 阿尔佛雷德\N{\fs40.9}Why are you being like this, Alfred?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.70,1:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天经受了可怕的考验\N{\fs40.9}I had a terrible ordeal today.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.72,1:19:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就失去了一样\N{\fs40.9}I thought that something very precious...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.25,1:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常宝贵的东西\N{\fs40.9}...had been lost to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.26,1:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想稍微庆祝一下\N{\fs40.9}So I just wanted to celebrate just a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.46,1:19:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 是什么 你差点失去了什么\N{\fs40.9}All right, what? What did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.07,1:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 又是秘密\N{\fs40.9}I see, more secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.57,1:19:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 秘密就是我的人生\N{\fs40.9}Sarah, secrets are my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.67,1:19:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们的人生  - 别这样了 阿尔弗雷德 停下来 这不是你\N{\fs40.9}- Our life. - No, Alfred, stop, this isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.01,1:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再演戏了\N{\fs40.9}Stop performing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.64,1:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为只有我一个人住这儿呢 布兰德先生\N{\fs40.9}I thought I had the place to myself, Mr. Brand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.21,1:20:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是不速之客 一点礼貌都没有\N{\fs40.9}Unexpected guests, not very polite.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.58,1:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还问了一大堆问题\N{\fs40.9}A lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.48,1:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始 我以为他们是政府的人\N{\fs40.9}At first, I thought they might work for the government.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.35,1:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不是吗  - 更糟 他们是爱迪生的人\N{\fs40.9}- No? - Worse, they work for Thomas Edison.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.99,1:20:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 发生了意想不到的事情\N{\fs40.9}Today, a most curious development.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.56,1:20:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的助手来找我们 还给我们提了个醒\N{\fs40.9}His assistant came to us with a proposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.26,1:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 是安吉尔派她来的 她的话也是他教她说的\N{\fs40.9}Obviously, Angier has sent her and told her to admit as much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.73,1:20:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他享受呆在台下向观众鞠躬致意吗\N{\fs40.9}Does he enjoy taking his bows under the stage?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.60,1:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他派我来窃取你的秘密\N{\fs40.9}He sent me here to steal your secrets,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.68,1:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实我要来把他的秘密告诉你\N{\fs40.9}but I've actually come to offer you his.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.44,1:20:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真相\N{\fs40.9}This is the truth...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.47,1:20:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fs40.9}...is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.70,1:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这些是他让我跟你说的 \N{\fs40.9}No, that's what he told me to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.91,1:20:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相是 我爱他 我一直站在他那边 \N{\fs40.9}The truth... ...is that I loved him and I stood by him
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.68,1:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却派我到你这儿来\N{\fs40.9}and he sent me to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.08,1:21:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像派一个舞台工作人员去帮他挑选穿什么衬衫一样\N{\fs40.9}like he would send a stagehand to pick up his shirts.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.76,1:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨他\N{\fs40.9}I hate him for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.43,1:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坐在剧院的最后一排就能看穿安吉尔的魔术\N{\fs40.9}I could spot Angier's methods from the back of the theater.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.64,1:21:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你还有什么可以告诉我的\N{\fs40.9}So, what could you possibly have to offer me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.28,1:21:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看穿了他的魔术\N{\fs40.9}You may know how he does his tricks,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.68,1:21:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却不知道 为什么人们认为你的魔术没他的好\N{\fs40.9}but you can't understand why no one sees that yours are better.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.74,1:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把手上的伤包起来了 \N{\fs40.9}You hide this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.78,1:21:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在表演"瞬间转移"的时候 \N{\fs40.9}I had to look very closely to spot it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.76,1:21:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得看得很仔细才能看出来\N{\fs40.9}when you performed the Transported Man.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.66,1:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这正是你的特别之处\N{\fs40.9}but this makes you unique.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.86,1:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向观众显示你并没有用替身\N{\fs40.9}It shows the audience you aren't using a double.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.86,1:21:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能把它藏起来 你得骄傲地展示出来\N{\fs40.9}You mustn't hide it. You must display it proudly.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.26,1:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢肯定仅用一只手完成魔术表演要难上加难\N{\fs40.9}I'm sure it takes great skill to perform illusions with one good hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.99,1:21:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的没错\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.53,1:21:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就让大家也知道啊\N{\fs40.9}So let people know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.77,1:21:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以比他做得好得多 我可以教你怎么做\N{\fs40.9}You can be so much more than he is and I can show you how.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.97,1:21:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她没有骗我\N{\fs40.9}I think she's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.64,1:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们还是不能信任她\N{\fs40.9}I think we cannot trust her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.54,1:21:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我爱她 我需要她\N{\fs40.9}But I love her. I need her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.98,1:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要维持这样一段感情\N{\fs40.9}To open myself to such a relationship,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.39,1:22:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险婚外恋\N{\fs40.9}to the dangers of such an affair,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.70,1:22:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要她向我保证她是忠诚的 是爱我的\N{\fs40.9}I need assurances of fidelity, of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.28,1:22:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这要如何确定呢\N{\fs40.9}But how to be sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.93,1:22:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一个办法 一个唯一能知道她的想法的办法\N{\fs40.9}I know a way. It's the only way to know her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.34,1:22:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么舍得派你过来呢\N{\fs40.9}How could he send you away?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.04,1:22:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她必须得帮我们摆脱安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}She must help me rid ourselves of Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.75,1:22:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我的情人证明了她的忠诚\N{\fs40.9}Today, my mistress proves her truthfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.82,1:22:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是向我证明 你懂的\N{\fs40.9}Not to me, you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.14,1:22:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她带我去找鲁特的时候 我就已经深知她的忠诚了\N{\fs40.9}I've been convinced since she led me to Root.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.50,1:22:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 奥利维向你证明了她对我的爱 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}Today, Olivia proves her love for me to you, Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.47,1:22:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 安吉尔 是我让她把日记带给你的\N{\fs40.9}Yes, Angier, she gave you this notebook at my request.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.06,1:22:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 "特斯拉"只是我日记的解锁关键词\N{\fs40.9}And yes, "Tesla" Is merely the key to my dairy,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.68,1:22:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我的魔术无关 \N{\fs40.9}not to my trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.22,1:23:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真认为我付出如此多后会这么容易把我的秘密拱手让人吗 \N{\fs40.9}Did you really think I'd part with my secret so easily after so much?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.04,1:23:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}Goodbye, Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.48,1:23:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你在遥远的美国追求抱负时能找到心灵的慰藉\N{\fs40.9}May you find solace for your forward ambition back in your American home.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.56,1:23:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉\N{\fs40.9}Tesla!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.78,1:23:17.41,6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45.444\frz3.455\b1\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fscx108\fscy100\c&H353341&\pos(1431.6,704.74)}有电危险{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.76,1:23:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉 阿利\N{\fs40.9}Tesla! Alley!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.44,1:23:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿利\N{\fs40.9}Alley!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.24,1:23:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉从未帮我造那台我要求的机器\N{\fs40.9}Tesla never made a machine like the one I asked for.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.91,1:23:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没说过他会造  \N{\fs40.9}I never said he had.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.73,1:23:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你让我认为他造了\N{\fs40.9}But you let me believe that he had.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.08,1:23:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们挪用我的钱 因为你们的资金被切断了\N{\fs40.9}You stole my money because your funding had been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.68,1:23:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在我的帽子上乱射一气\N{\fs40.9}You've been shooting sparks in my top hat,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.68,1:23:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗中嘲笑我 还用我的钱去补你们的亏空\N{\fs40.9}laughing at me all along, while using my money to stave off ruin.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.28,1:23:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我可看到爱迪生的人了  - 在哪儿\N{\fs40.9}- I have seen Edison's men. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.14,1:23:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在酒店里 我现在随时可以把他们带过来\N{\fs40.9}In the hotel, I've every mind to bring them up here myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.70,1:23:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做是不明智的 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}That would be unwise, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.72,1:23:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 你是我们最后的金主了\N{\fs40.9}It is true that you are our last remaining financier,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.60,1:23:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们没有挪用你的钱\N{\fs40.9}but we have not stolen your money.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.53,1:23:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的猫\N{\fs40.9}This is my, uh, my cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.07,1:23:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我告诉你我可以为你造一台机器时 我说的是实话\N{\fs40.9}When I told you I could make you a machine, I spoke a simple truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.36,1:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机器为什么不管用\N{\fs40.9}Then why isn't the machine working?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.86,1:24:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为科学 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}Because exact science, Mr. Angier,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.92,1:24:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学有时并不严密\N{\fs40.9}is not an exact science.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.64,1:24:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器并没有像我们期待的那样运作\N{\fs40.9}The machine simply does not operate as expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.82,1:24:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还需要对它进行进一步的检测  \N{\fs40.9}It requires further examination.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.00,1:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我的帽子去哪儿了\N{\fs40.9}So where did my top hat go?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.72,1:24:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在这儿\N{\fs40.9}Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.02,1:24:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这个该死的机器试了十几遍\N{\fs40.9}We tried the damn thing a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.76,1:24:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子还是纹丝不动\N{\fs40.9}The hat went nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.12,1:24:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算尝试不同的材料\N{\fs40.9}We need to try different material.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.26,1:24:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会有不同的结果\N{\fs40.9}It may provoke a different result.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.06,1:24:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs40.9}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.77,1:24:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只猫要是有什么三长两短 你得负责 博士\N{\fs40.9}You are responsible for whatever happens to this animal, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.26,1:25:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望你能真正把我的钱用到实处 特斯拉先生\N{\fs40.9}I hope whatever you were really doing with my money was more worthwhile, Mr. Tesla.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.32,1:25:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿利\N{\fs40.9}Alley!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.39,1:26:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以机器的运作是正常的\N{\fs40.9}So the machine was working?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.20,1:26:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过去测量尺寸的问题 \N{\fs40.9}I never bothered to check the calibration,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.15,1:26:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为帽子一直就在那没动过\N{\fs40.9}'cause the hat never moved.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.90,1:26:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西的发展完全出乎你的意料 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}These things never quite work as you expect them to, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.84,1:26:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是科学的魅力之一啊\N{\fs40.9}That's one of the principal beauties of science.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.41,1:26:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要几个星期的时间\N{\fs40.9}I'll need a couple of weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.76,1:26:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来解决机器目前存在的问题\N{\fs40.9}to iron out the problems with the machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.80,1:26:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了我们会通知你的\N{\fs40.9}We'll send word when it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.38,1:26:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了你的帽子\N{\fs40.9}Don't forget your hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.25,1:26:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一顶是我的  \N{\fs40.9}Well, which one is mine?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.28,1:26:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一顶都是你的 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}They are all your hats, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.93,1:26:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着新裙子好漂亮呀\N{\fs40.9}You look so pretty in this new dress of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.00,1:26:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们下午去动物园吗  \N{\fs40.9}Are we going to the zoo this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.48,1:26:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 爸爸还有事要做\N{\fs40.9}No, remember daddy has some errands to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.02,1:26:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但你答应过的  - 我答应过 是吗\N{\fs40.9}- But you promised. - I promised, did I?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.48,1:26:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就去动物园喽\N{\fs40.9}Then go to the zoo, we shall.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.64,1:26:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸先去办事\N{\fs40.9}Daddy will go run his errands,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.90,1:26:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就回来\N{\fs40.9}and I'll be back before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.24,1:26:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去准备 我们去看大猩猩\N{\fs40.9}So you go get ready. We'll go see those chimpanzees.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.85,1:26:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 你这是干什么\N{\fs40.9}Sarah... what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.18,1:27:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都有恶习\N{\fs40.9}Each of us have our vices.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.03,1:27:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉 不管你是怎么想的\N{\fs40.9}Sarah, whatever you may think...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.07,1:27:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可能来争夺我对你的爱的 只有我们的女儿\N{\fs40.9}...your only competition for my affections is our little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.77,1:27:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 我永远爱你\N{\fs40.9}I love you. I will always love you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.81,1:27:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只爱你一人\N{\fs40.9}and you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.11,1:27:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你今天说的是真话  - 当然\N{\fs40.9}- You mean it today. - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.24,1:27:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只让我在你说假话的那些日子里更加难过\N{\fs40.9}Which makes it so much harder when you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.16,1:27:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,购物清单更长了 她可真能花钱\N{\fs40.9}More shopping. She does love the smell of money, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.03,1:27:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小家伙想去动物园\N{\fs40.9}The little lady wants to go to the zoo,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.00,1:27:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你能带她去吧\N{\fs40.9}so I thought you could take her, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.52,1:27:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不行 就我明天带她去\N{\fs40.9}I mean, I can do it tomorrow, if not.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.06,1:27:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 莎拉\N{\fs40.9}And, uh... Sarah,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.21,1:27:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道了\N{\fs40.9}she knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.68,1:27:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她至少是知道有些事不对劲\N{\fs40.9}Uh, I mean at least she knows that something is not right,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.82,1:28:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你能尽量帮帮我吗\N{\fs40.9}so if you can just do whatever you can to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.78,1:28:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她聊聊 让她相信我真的爱她\N{\fs40.9}Talk to her, try and convince her that I do love her.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.10,1:28:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 弗雷迪\N{\fs40.9}What is it, Freddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.87,1:28:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样叫我 行吗\N{\fs40.9}Listen, don't call me that, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.10,1:28:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 就是有时候感觉这样不太好\N{\fs40.9}It's nothing. It's just that sometimes something just seems wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.38,1:28:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过 你跟我在一起时 就想着我\N{\fs40.9}I told you, when you're with me, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.90,1:28:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再去想你的家人\N{\fs40.9}Leave your family at home where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.84,1:28:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在努力 我在努力 奥利维娅\N{\fs40.9}I'm trying. I'm trying, Olivia.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.18,1:28:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我去梳妆  - 好\N{\fs40.9}- I'll get dressed. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.05,1:28:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又看到法隆在这周围徘徊了\N{\fs40.9}I saw Fallon hanging around again.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.74,1:28:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点不信任那个人\N{\fs40.9}There's something about that man I don't trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.86,1:28:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你信任我吗 那就信任法隆\N{\fs40.9}You trust me? Then trust Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.24,1:28:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保护我珍视的东西\N{\fs40.9}He protects the things that I care about.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.64,1:29:16.52,2,,0,0,0,,{\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs45.444\c&H756571&\frz287.4\3c&H322E61&\pos(1210.8,397.28)}有电危险
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.73,1:29:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对您的离别感到遗憾 安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}We're sorry to see you go, Mr. Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.30,1:29:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也对特斯拉先生的离去感到遗憾\N{\fs40.9}We were sorry to see Mr. Tesla leave, as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.94,1:29:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为科罗拉多泉做了很多好事\N{\fs40.9}He's very good to Colorado Springs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.70,1:29:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔先生\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Angier,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.84,1:29:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为您没必要向爱迪生的人说那个箱子的事\N{\fs40.9}I didn't think it was necessary to tell Edison's men about the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.24,1:29:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么箱子\N{\fs40.9}What box?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.72,1:30:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉不告而别\N{\fs40.9}I apologize for leaving without saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.44,1:30:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但科罗拉多似乎已经不再欢迎我了\N{\fs40.9}But I seem to have outstayed my welcome in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.44,1:30:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在科学和工业领域 真正的非凡成就往往会遭到打压\N{\fs40.9}The truly extraordinary is not permitted in science and industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.89,1:30:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在你的领域 情况会好些\N{\fs40.9}Perhaps you'll find more luck in your field,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.46,1:30:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的领域 人们都心甘情愿地被迷惑\N{\fs40.9}where people are happy to be mystified.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.68,1:30:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的东西就在这个箱子里\N{\fs40.9}You will find what you are looking for in this box.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.88,1:30:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿利已经为你写了一份详尽的使用说明\N{\fs40.9}Alley has written you a thorough set of instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.18,1:30:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这台机器的使用 我只加一点\N{\fs40.9}I add only one suggestion on using the machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.84,1:30:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁掉它吧\N{\fs40.9}Destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.08,1:30:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它扔到最深的海底\N{\fs40.9}Drop it to the bottom of the deepest ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.40,1:30:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只会给你带来无尽的痛苦\N{\fs40.9}Such a thing will bring you only misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.52,1:30:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特斯拉也知道 自己的警告是多么的苍白无力\N{\fs40.9}Tesla's warning is as unheeded as he knew it would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.96,1:30:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我对机器进行了测试 \N{\fs40.9}Today I tested the machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.20,1:31:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我事先采取了预防措施 \N{\fs40.9}Taking precautions in case Tesla hadn't ironed out
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.12,1:31:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防特斯拉还没有解决机器的运作故障问题\N{\fs40.9}the kinks in its operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.80,1:31:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一运作不顺利\N{\fs40.9}But if it went wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.77,1:31:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不愿意拖着残躯苟延残喘的\N{\fs40.9}I would not want to live like that for long.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.39,1:31:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在 我必须跟你说再见了 波顿\N{\fs40.9}But here at the turn, I must leave you, Borden.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.59,1:31:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是你 波顿\N{\fs40.9}Yes, you, Borden,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.89,1:31:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐在牢房里\N{\fs40.9}sitting there in your cell,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.33,1:31:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读着我的日记 以谋杀我的罪名\N{\fs40.9}reading my diary, awaiting your death,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.43,1:31:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待着死亡\N{\fs40.9}for my murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.77,1:31:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔的日记 不是拿它来显示诚意的吗 它是假的\N{\fs40.9}Angier's journal, that gesture of good faith, that's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.14,1:31:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证 它是真的\N{\fs40.9}I assure you, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.51,1:31:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那本日记来历清楚 没什么好怀疑的\N{\fs40.9}The provenance of the journal is clear and under no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.52,1:31:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是安吉尔亲手写的\N{\fs40.9}And it's written in Angier's own hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.82,1:32:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有他的其它文稿可作证明\N{\fs40.9}for which we have numerous examples.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.89,1:32:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便吧\N{\fs40.9}It don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.73,1:32:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的魔术\N{\fs40.9}So my tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.00,1:32:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的魔术  \N{\fs40.9}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.55,1:32:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括"瞬间转移"吗\N{\fs40.9}Including The Transported Man?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.90,1:32:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 卡德罗勋爵会很高兴的  - 不 他不会\N{\fs40.9}- Lord Caldlow will be very pleased indeed. - No, he won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.17,1:32:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都不完整\N{\fs40.9}They're not complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.61,1:32:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个魔术都只有"暗度陈仓"和"风云变色"两部分\N{\fs40.9}It's just the Pledge and the Turn for each.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.68,1:32:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有"拨云见日"的部分 它们一文不值\N{\fs40.9}Without the Prestige for these tricks, these are worthless.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.70,1:32:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40.9}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.78,1:32:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我女儿带来 我就把剩下的部分交给你\N{\fs40.9}You get the rest of it... when you bring my daughter here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.10,1:32:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟她告别\N{\fs40.9}I want to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.89,1:32:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天必须得说清楚 我们今天必须得说清楚\N{\fs40.9}We have to go through it now. We have to go through it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.13,1:32:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 你就尽情抵赖吧\N{\fs40.9}Now, listen to me, deny it all you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.57,1:32:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利维娅根本不算什么\N{\fs40.9}Olivia means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.88,1:32:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 奥利维娅  - 我需要一个助手 我不能没有助手\N{\fs40.9}- Olivia? - I need an assistant. I can't not have an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.60,1:32:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要去找她  我要告诉她  - 告诉她什么\N{\fs40.9}- I'll go to her, I'll tell her. - You'll tell her what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.96,1:32:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的真面目了 阿尔弗雷德\N{\fs40.9}I know what you really are, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.94,1:33:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我知道了  - 莎拉 莎拉 莎拉\N{\fs40.9}- I know. - Sarah, Sarah, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.20,1:33:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我不能就这么把这事埋在心里  - 你别再胡说八道了\N{\fs40.9}- I can't keep it in. - You can't talk like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.48,1:33:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 不  -  莎拉 闭嘴  莎拉 闭嘴\N{\fs40.9}- No. No. - Sarah, shut up! Sarah, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.40,1:33:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再听你说下去了 你别再胡说八道了\N{\fs40.9}I don't want to hear it anymore. You can't talk like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.83,1:33:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法再保守这个秘密了 因为我知道了 阿尔弗雷德 我知道了\N{\fs40.9}You can't hide it anymore, because I know, Alfred, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.30,1:33:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的真面目了 阿尔弗雷德\N{\fs40.9}I know what you really are, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.80,1:33:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再这样过下去\N{\fs40.9}I can't live like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.67,1:33:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我可以这样过下去吗\N{\fs40.9}Oh, well, you think I can live like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.87,1:33:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我现在这样过得很自在吗\N{\fs40.9}You think I bloody enjoy living like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.11,1:33:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拥有漂亮的大房子 可爱的女儿 我们是夫妻\N{\fs40.9}We have this beautiful house, lovely little girl, we're married.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.58,1:33:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有什么不满足\N{\fs40.9}What is so wrong with your life?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.31,1:33:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德 我没法再这样过下去了\N{\fs40.9}Alfred, I can't live like this!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.98,1:33:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想要什么\N{\fs40.9}Well, what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.69,1:33:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我想\N{\fs40.9}I... I want...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.46,1:33:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你 对我说实话\N{\fs40.9}I want you to be... honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.26,1:33:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不耍心眼\N{\fs40.9}No tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.80,1:33:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不撒谎\N{\fs40.9}No lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.97,1:33:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有秘密\N{\fs40.9}And no secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.22,1:34:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你爱我吗\N{\fs40.9}Do you... do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.45,1:34:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不爱\N{\fs40.9}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.22,1:34:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不爱\N{\fs40.9}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.86,1:35:28.12,1,,0,0,0,,{\fn钟齐吴嘉睿手写字\fs34.083\c&H14141A&\b1\frz0.1019\pos(1214.4,365.373)}艾德威驰街230号{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.86,1:35:28.12,1,,0,0,0,,{\fn钟齐吴嘉睿手写字\fs34.083\b1\c&H0F0D14&\frz2.124\pos(1227,471.348)}伦敦{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.92,1:35:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在那儿\N{\fs40.9}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.38,1:36:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来找一位老朋友\N{\fs40.9}I'm looking for an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.56,1:36:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说有人预定了场地 是个不赖的小剧院\N{\fs40.9}I heard about a booking, nice little theater,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.26,1:36:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他是个很有前途的魔术师  - 你回来了\N{\fs40.9}- good up-and-coming magician. - You're back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.12,1:36:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 约翰\N{\fs40.9}It's good to see you, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.36,1:36:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个彩排地点不错\N{\fs40.9}Good rehearsal space.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.14,1:36:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盲人工作人员 我喜欢\N{\fs40.9}Blind stagehands, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.94,1:36:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总能找到宣传的噱头\N{\fs40.9}You always had a good eye for publicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.50,1:36:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙 约翰\N{\fs40.9}I need your help, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.48,1:36:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要办最后一轮演出 限制场次\N{\fs40.9}It's my last show. A limited engagement.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.10,1:36:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一轮演出\N{\fs40.9}Your last show?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.10,1:36:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个聪明人曾经告诉过我 痴迷是年轻人的游戏\N{\fs40.9}A wise man once told me obsession was a young man's game.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.68,1:36:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要退休了 但还有一个心愿未了结\N{\fs40.9}I'm almost done. There's one thing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.44,1:36:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是表演真正的"瞬间转移"\N{\fs40.9}The Real Transported Man.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.59,1:36:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想以此作为你表演的噱头吗\N{\fs40.9}You want to design a show around it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.66,1:36:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想你呆在后台 我需要你替我在前方进行经营\N{\fs40.9}I don't want you backstage I need you in front the house managing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.60,1:36:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你调动你所有的人际关系\N{\fs40.9}I need you to call in any favors or connections you have left
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.33,1:36:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我们订到合适的剧场\N{\fs40.9}to get us the right booking for the run.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.28,1:36:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想订什么样的\N{\fs40.9}What sort of booking you after?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.28,1:36:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让波顿无法注意不到的\N{\fs40.9}The sort that Borden can't ignore.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.96,1:37:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 能再次见到您是多么荣幸啊 先生\N{\fs40.9}Oh, what an honor it is to see you again, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.76,1:37:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我说 你只想向我表演一个魔术\N{\fs40.9}You told me you only wanted to show me one trick
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.84,1:37:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这引起了我的兴趣\N{\fs40.9} that'd pique my interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.00,1:37:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个魔术相当新颖 阿克曼先生  \N{\fs40.9}It's a very clever trick. Mr.Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.40,1:37:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 阿克曼先生\N{\fs40.9}Pleased to meet you, Mr. Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.56,1:37:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 我们开始吧\N{\fs40.9}Likewise, I'm sure. Let's get on, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.30,1:37:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动吧 先生们\N{\fs40.9}Turn it on, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.90,1:37:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺吸引人眼球的\N{\fs40.9}Very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.32,1:37:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就完了吗 卡特 他就只是这么消失而已吗\N{\fs40.9}That's it, Cutter? He simply disappears?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.98,1:37:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能算魔术 他必须得再次出现\N{\fs40.9}That's not a trick. He has to come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.96,1:37:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 缺了一部分  - "拨云见日"\N{\fs40.9}- There has to be a... - A prestige?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.16,1:37:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是\N{\fs40.9}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.70,1:37:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我\N{\fs40.9}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.50,1:37:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今真正的魔术表演\N{\fs40.9}It's very rare to see...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.56,1:37:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太少了\N{\fs40.9}...real magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.80,1:37:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很多年没有看到过\N{\fs40.9}It's been many years since I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.64,1:37:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意助我们一臂之力吗\N{\fs40.9}Are you interested in helping us?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.28,1:38:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意 但你们得把它包装一下\N{\fs40.9}Yes... but you'll have to dress it up a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.28,1:38:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对它进行伪装\N{\fs40.9}Disguise it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.64,1:38:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让观众有足够的理由对此进行怀疑和探究\N{\fs40.9}Give them enough reason to doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.90,1:38:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到现在为止还没提起过她 弗雷迪 一个字都没有\N{\fs40.9}You haven't spoken about her, Freddie, not once.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.28,1:38:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要跟你谈论她呢\N{\fs40.9}Why would I talk about her to you, hm?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.12,1:38:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是你生命中的一部分 现在她去世了\N{\fs40.9}Because she was a part of your life and now she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.82,1:38:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她自杀的前一天 \N{\fs40.9}You know, the day before she killed herself
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.50,1:38:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说想约我出来见个面\N{\fs40.9}she said she wanted to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.24,1:38:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说有些关于你的事要告诉我\N{\fs40.9}That she had something to tell me about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.24,1:38:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太胆小了 不敢去面对她\N{\fs40.9}I was such a coward, I couldn't bring myself to face her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.91,1:38:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs40.9}But...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.14,1:38:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本来想跟我说什么呢\N{\fs40.9}...what would she have said?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.95,1:38:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道真相吗\N{\fs40.9}You want to know the truth about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.32,1:38:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相是\N{\fs40.9}The truth is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.99,1:38:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未爱过莎拉\N{\fs40.9}...I never loved Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.90,1:38:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未爱过她\N{\fs40.9}I never loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.72,1:38:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她是夫妻 还生了一个孩子\N{\fs40.9}You married her, you had a child with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.26,1:39:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 那只是一部分的我 一部分的我心在她身上 但是\N{\fs40.9}Yes. Part of me. Part of me did, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.24,1:39:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的另一部分不是这样\N{\fs40.9}...the other part didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.24,1:39:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一部分找到了你 这一部分现在就坐在你面前\N{\fs40.9}The part that found you, the part that's sitting here right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.54,1:39:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 别不相信 奥利维娅 我爱你\N{\fs40.9}I love you. No, Olivia, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.88,1:39:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是真相\N{\fs40.9}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.71,1:39:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正值得注意的真相\N{\fs40.9}That is the truth that matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.18,1:39:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在也完全可能\N{\fs40.9}You could be in some other
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.84,1:39:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在另一家餐厅\N{\fs40.9}restaurant with some other woman right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.65,1:39:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟另一个女人说着我的坏话\N{\fs40.9}talking about me that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.32,1:39:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不会的  - 就是这样\N{\fs40.9}- No. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.89,1:39:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直冷血得不近人情\N{\fs40.9}It's inhuman to be so cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.78,1:39:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了\N{\fs40.9}He's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.47,1:39:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了两年 他又有新魔术了\N{\fs40.9}After two years, he's got a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.81,1:39:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都说那是伦敦有史以来最好的魔术\N{\fs40.9}They're saying it's the best London's ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.68,1:39:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真应该看看自己脸上的表情 "教授"\N{\fs40.9}You should see the look on your face, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.02,1:39:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该去找他\N{\fs40.9}You should go to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.02,1:39:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩还真是物以类聚\N{\fs40.9}You two deserve each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.74,1:40:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我这儿都已经预定满了\N{\fs40.9}But I'm afraid I'm booked.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.40,1:40:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科芭蕾舞团 他们的表演要一直持续到明年呢\N{\fs40.9}The Moscow Ballet, they'll be playing through next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.68,1:40:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就打发他们走吧\N{\fs40.9}Then get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.90,1:40:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共一百场演出 一场不多 一场不少\N{\fs40.9}There will be 100 performances, no more, no less.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.17,1:40:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每周五场 全是夜场演出\N{\fs40.9}Five performances a week, no matinees.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.47,1:40:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每张门票这个价 祝你愉快\N{\fs40.9}That's what you'll be charging for each ticket. Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.42,1:40:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 我今晚的第一个魔术\N{\fs40.9}Ladies and gentlemen, my first trick of the evening
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.58,1:40:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在潜在的危险\N{\fs40.9}is one that involves considerable risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.26,1:40:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你看到人在自己面前淹死 \N{\fs40.9}Anyone in the audience who would be irrevocably damaged
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.17,1:40:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会感到严重不适 就请现在离场\N{\fs40.9}by seeing a man drown should leave now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.44,1:40:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教给我水箱逃生魔术的那位女士\N{\fs40.9}When I tell you the lady who taught me this illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.90,1:40:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就因表演这个魔术而死\N{\fs40.9}actually died performing it,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.82,1:40:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说 相信你已经对潜在的危险有了一定了解\N{\fs40.9}you'll understand the seriousness of the dangers involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fs40.9}Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.63,1:41:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的旅途中 我看到了未来的样子\N{\fs40.9}In my travels, I have seen the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.07,1:41:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有着奇怪的景象\N{\fs40.9}And it is a strange future, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.74,1:41:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界 女士们先生们\N{\fs40.9}The world, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.14,1:41:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正处于更新换代的边缘\N{\fs40.9}is on the brink of new
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.52,1:41:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面临着种种恐怖的可能性\N{\fs40.9}and terrifying possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.57,1:41:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们即将看到的并不是魔术\N{\fs40.9}What you're about to witness is not magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.32,1:41:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是纯粹的科学\N{\fs40.9}It's purely science.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.14,1:41:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请你们走上舞台\N{\fs40.9}I'd like to invite you to come up on stage now
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.22,1:42:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己检验一下这台机器\N{\fs40.9}so that you can examine the machine for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.14,1:42:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类之所及\N{\fs40.9}Man's reach
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.70,1:43:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远超乎想象\N{\fs40.9}exceeds his imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.04,1:43:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs40.9}Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.20,1:43:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百场演出 为什么是一百场\N{\fs40.9}One hundred performances. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.20,1:43:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为他的魔术表演方式所限吗\N{\fs40.9}Does his method dictate that?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.72,1:43:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一种宣传手段 到底是什么\N{\fs40.9}Is it a publicity move? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.74,1:43:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是个草包魔术师 \N{\fs40.9}He's a no-talent magician,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.30,1:43:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却被人称为全英格兰最棒的魔术师 为什么\N{\fs40.9}and they call him the bloody best in England. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.58,1:43:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在一秒内移动了五十码 一秒钟\N{\fs40.9}Fifty yards in a second! In a second!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.44,1:43:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们唯一知道的就是他用了活板门\N{\fs40.9}And all that we know is he uses a trap door.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.20,1:43:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了 他在舞台下面动了什么手脚 啊\N{\fs40.9}Brilliant! What is going on under that stage? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.94,1:43:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你就想不到\N{\fs40.9}Why can't you out-think him?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.40,1:44:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每天晚上表演结束都会这样 对吗\N{\fs40.9}They do this every night, after each performance. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.06,1:44:33.73,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz346.1\fs56.806\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\c&H1F1D24&\fscx128\fscy96\pos(1232.001,209.142)}伟大的丹东
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.77,1:44:34.35,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.1\fs45.444\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fscx84\fscy130\c&H202327&\b1\pos(955.999,494.561)}真正的\N瞬间\N{\c&H212324&}转移{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.85,1:44:34.35,4,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.7\fn造字工房力黑（非商用）常规体\fs45.444\c&H202327&\b1\fscx96\fscy128\pos(1219.001,542.337)}仅\N100\N场{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.76,1:44:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧\N{\fs40.9}We're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.54,1:44:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs40.9}All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.44,1:44:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他表演去吧\N{\fs40.9}Let him have his trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.08,1:44:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要他的秘密\N{\fs40.9}I don't need, I don't need his secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.84,1:44:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs40.9}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.82,1:44:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再去那儿看他演出了 别再管他\N{\fs40.9}...don't go back there, you leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.84,1:44:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我俩都 别再管他了\N{\fs40.9}Both of us... just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.02,1:44:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止\N{\fs40.9}We're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.62,1:45:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 约翰\N{\fs40.9}I told you, John.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.70,1:45:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望你在这个表演魔术时到后台来\N{\fs40.9}I don't want you backstage on this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.66,1:45:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我邀请你们走上舞台\N{\fs40.9}I would like to invite you to come up onstage now
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.80,1:45:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己检验一下这台机器\N{\fs40.9}so that you can examine the machine for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.64,1:45:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你往哪儿走呢\N{\fs40.9}Hey, where do you think...?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.23,1:45:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这该死演出的一份子 蠢货\N{\fs40.9}I'm part of the bloody act, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.70,1:46:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那是谁\N{\fs40.9}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.28,1:47:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 该死的钥匙在哪\N{\fs40.9}Hey! Where's the bloody key?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.15,1:47:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该死的钥匙在哪\N{\fs40.9}Where's the bloody key?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.15,1:47:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的钥匙在哪 他要淹死了\N{\fs40.9}Where's the bloody key?! He's bloody drowning!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.13,1:47:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\fs40.9}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.74,1:47:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\fs40.9}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.82,1:47:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德·波顿 \N{\fs40.9}Alfred Borden,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.34,1:47:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因谋杀罗伯特·安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}you have been found guilty of the murder of Robert Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.40,1:47:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被判处绞刑\N{\fs40.9}You will be hanged by the neck until dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.76,1:47:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿主宽恕你的灵魂\N{\fs40.9}May the Lord have mercy on your soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.36,1:48:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特先生\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Cutter?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.84,1:48:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是欧文斯\N{\fs40.9}Owens.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.88,1:48:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 谢谢你专门来一趟 欧文斯先生\N{\fs40.9}Oh, thank you for coming, Mr. Owens.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.30,1:48:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来是负责处理安吉尔先生的道具的\N{\fs40.9}It has fallen to me to dispose of Mr. Angier's equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.76,1:48:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我发现这张清单显示\N{\fs40.9}But I notice from this manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.42,1:48:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡德罗勋爵把他的大部分道具都出钱买下了\N{\fs40.9}that Lord Caldlow has purchased the bulk of the items.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.99,1:48:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特先生 如果你是需要这些货物的送货地址的话\N{\fs40.9}Mr. Cutter, if you need to know where to deliver these items...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.36,1:48:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是这儿有一样道具\N{\fs40.9}No, it's just there is one particular item,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.90,1:48:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个道具 其实\N{\fs40.9}this item, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.57,1:48:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我想  - 你想\N{\fs40.9}- that I would like to... - You would like to...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.90,1:48:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买下来\N{\fs40.9}...buy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.07,1:48:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 自己买下来吗  - 嗯 我是这么想的\N{\fs40.9}- Buy yourself? - Yeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.21,1:48:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这就是那台机器吗  - 没错\N{\fs40.9}- This is the machine? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.38,1:48:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恐怕不行 卡德罗勋爵已经特别指明 \N{\fs40.9}Well, I'm afraid Lord Caldlow was adamant about
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.82,1:48:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要把它买下来\N{\fs40.9}purchasing this particular item.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.32,1:48:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你看我能跟卡德罗勋爵当面谈谈吗\N{\fs40.9}Do you think I could talk to Lord Caldlow in person?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.46,1:48:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕不可能\N{\fs40.9}Out of the question, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.19,1:48:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fs40.9}Of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.42,1:48:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你在安排送货的时候\N{\fs40.9}I suppose if, in the course of your delivery arrangements,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.32,1:48:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧遇到了他 \N{\fs40.9}your paths were to cross,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.20,1:49:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时你要上去跟他攀谈 那我也不好阻止你\N{\fs40.9}I can't stop you speaking your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.06,1:49:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs40.9}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.60,1:49:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还没逃出去呢 波顿  - 暂时而已\N{\fs40.9}- Still here, Borden? - For now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.58,1:49:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来看你了 卡德罗勋爵\N{\fs40.9}You got a visitor. Lord Caldlow.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.70,1:49:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还带着个小女孩\N{\fs40.9}With a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.00,1:49:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\fs40.9}Jess?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.78,1:49:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊 亲爱的\N{\fs40.9}Hello, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.98,1:49:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好么 我好想你\N{\fs40.9}How are you? I've missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.16,1:49:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法隆也很想你 我们都想\N{\fs40.9}Fallon's missed you too. We both have.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.20,1:49:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我能进去吗\N{\fs40.9}Daddy, can I come in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.34,1:49:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行 现在不行 亲爱的\N{\fs40.9}Not right now. Not right now, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.87,1:49:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但一切都会好起来的\N{\fs40.9}No, but everything is gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.71,1:49:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定就是卡德罗勋爵了吧\N{\fs40.9}You must be Lord Caldlow?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.51,1:49:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔多罗 没错 就是我\N{\fs40.9}Caldlow. Yes, I am. I always have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.28,1:49:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是怕了你了 给你戴那么多锁链 阿尔弗雷德\N{\fs40.9}They flatter you with all those chains, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.55,1:49:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他们不知道 你离了那个小橡皮球就没法脱身吗\N{\fs40.9}Don't they know you can't escape without your little rubber ball?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.65,1:49:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲手把你 把你从水箱里弄出来\N{\fs40.9}I pulled you out... out of that tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.72,1:50:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一想做的 就是证明我是一个比你优秀的魔术师\N{\fs40.9}All I wanted to do was prove that I was a better magician.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.63,1:50:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就是不肯让我安生\N{\fs40.9}But you couldn't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.03,1:50:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么弄的\N{\fs40.9}I don't know what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.04,1:50:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你已经不怕弄脏手了 对吗\N{\fs40.9}But you're not afraid to get your hands dirty anymore, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.81,1:50:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 再也不怕了 而且我赢了\N{\fs40.9}No, not anymore. And I win.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.14,1:50:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在乎躲在台下的人 那个消失不见的人\N{\fs40.9}There's no one that cares about the man in the box, the man who disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.55,1:50:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了\N{\fs40.9}You win?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.12,1:50:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经不是什么竞争了 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}This ain't a bloody competition anymore, Angier.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.78,1:50:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这关乎我女儿的人生\N{\fs40.9}This is my little girl's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.85,1:50:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别想让她搅这潭浑水\N{\fs40.9}And don't you dare put her in the middle of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.92,1:50:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 失去心爱的人到底有多么痛\N{\fs40.9}Oh, I know how hard it is to have someone so special
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.99,1:50:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可知道得清清楚楚 你说是吗 波顿\N{\fs40.9}taken away from you, don't I, Borden?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.36,1:50:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在她的去向已经不由你决定了 对吧\N{\fs40.9}And you can't take her with you, now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.17,1:50:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会受到很好的照料的\N{\fs40.9}Oh, she'll be looked after.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.13,1:50:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 "教授" 走了 亲爱的\N{\fs40.9}Goodbye, Professor. Come on, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.24,1:50:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不 别走 亲爱的 停下来\N{\fs40.9}No, no, no, no, stop, my darling, stop, stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.12,1:50:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 给你\N{\fs40.9}Look, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.74,1:50:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你一直想要的东西 你费尽心思就是为了这个\N{\fs40.9}That's what you're after. That's what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.81,1:50:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着吧\N{\fs40.9}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.25,1:50:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你的秘密  - 嗯\N{\fs40.9}- Your secret? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.15,1:51:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你才是那个更优秀的魔术师 我们都心知肚明\N{\fs40.9}You always were the better magician. We both know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.36,1:51:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但无论你的秘密是什么 你不得不承认\N{\fs40.9}Whatever your secret was, you have to agree,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.09,1:51:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的要更好\N{\fs40.9}mine is better.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:11.13,1:51:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 别这样 安吉尔 不 杰西 杰西\N{\fs40.9}Don't do this. Don't do this, Angier. No. Jess, Jess!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.57,1:51:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西 我马上就会去接你回家的 我保证\N{\fs40.9}Jess, I'm gonna take you home soon. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.17,1:51:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 看在老天的份儿上  - 我保证 看\N{\fs40.9}- For God's sake. - I promise. Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.58,1:51:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证 我爱你 杰西\N{\fs40.9}I promise. I love you, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.25,1:51:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs40.9}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.98,1:51:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 走吧  - 我爱你\N{\fs40.9}- Come on. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.68,1:51:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你 杰西\N{\fs40.9}I love you, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.45,1:51:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}Angier! Angier!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.86,1:51:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这个地方可以关住我吗\N{\fs40.9}What, do you think this place can hold me?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.02,1:51:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉尔 他们要绞死我\N{\fs40.9}Angier! They're gonna bloody hang me!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.28,1:51:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要绞死我 你明明可以停止这一切\N{\fs40.9}They're gonna bloody hang me! And you can put a stop to this now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.30,1:51:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 听我说 那个人\N{\fs40.9}Listen! Listen! That man...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.57,1:51:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 他们说我杀了那个人\N{\fs40.9}Listen, that man is the one I'm in for killing!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.00,1:51:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 他还活着 我没罪\N{\fs40.9}Listen! If he's alive, I'm not guilty!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.41,1:51:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我没罪  - 我才不管呢\N{\fs40.9}- I'm not guilty! - I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.14,1:51:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 抓住他  - 安吉尔\N{\fs40.9}- Get hold of him. - Angier!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.52,1:52:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs40.9}Run along now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.15,1:52:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 有位先生在等您\N{\fs40.9}Sir, there's a gentleman waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.50,1:52:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 老天啊  - 你好 卡特\N{\fs40.9}- Dear God. - Hello, Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.70,1:52:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着\N{\fs40.9}You're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.90,1:52:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能还活着 罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}How is it you're still alive, Robert?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.65,1:52:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看你躺在停尸床上了 看在老天的份上\N{\fs40.9}I saw you on a slab, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.05,1:52:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 孩子  - 晚安 先生\N{\fs40.9}- Child. - Good night, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.15,1:52:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 杰西\N{\fs40.9}Good night, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.36,1:52:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过那孩子\N{\fs40.9}I've seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.09,1:52:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在法庭上看到她\N{\fs40.9}I saw her in court with...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.82,1:52:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟法隆在一起\N{\fs40.9}...Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.30,1:52:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你都做了些什么  - 她需要人照顾\N{\fs40.9}- What have you done? - She needs looking after.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.12,1:52:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要她的父亲\N{\fs40.9}She needs her father.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.80,1:53:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样任由他被绞死 而我成了你的帮凶\N{\fs40.9}You're letting him hang, and I helped you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.74,1:53:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这儿 本来是要恳求卡德罗勋爵 \N{\fs40.9}I came here to beg Lord Caldlow
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.22,1:53:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许我把那台机器毁掉\N{\fs40.9}to let me destroy that machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.98,1:53:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不会求你任何事\N{\fs40.9}I am not going to beg you for anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.78,1:53:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必求我 我会保证那台机器永远不会再启用\N{\fs40.9}You don't have to. I'm gonna make sure that machine is never used again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.89,1:53:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 卡德罗勋爵\N{\fs40.9}Then, Lord Caldlow...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.53,1:53:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我把它送到哪里\N{\fs40.9}...where do you want me to deliver it?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.98,1:53:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的剧院 跟我其他的道具放在一起\N{\fs40.9}My theater. It belongs with the prestige materials.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.06,1:53:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰 我本来不想让你卷进来的\N{\fs40.9}John, I tried not to involve you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.45,1:53:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样了\N{\fs40.9}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.75,1:53:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要各走各的路了\N{\fs40.9}We go alone now.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.42,1:53:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来都要一个人走了\N{\fs40.9}Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.92,1:53:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的路就到此为止了\N{\fs40.9}I mean, I don't have as far to go as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.74,1:54:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别难过\N{\fs40.9}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.24,1:54:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对的 我不应该再去招惹他和他的魔术的\N{\fs40.9}You were right. I should have left him to his damn trick.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.26,1:54:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.71,1:54:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多事我都要说对不起\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry for a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.42,1:54:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对不起莎拉\N{\fs40.9}I'm sorry about Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.26,1:54:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过要伤害她 真的\N{\fs40.9}Didn't mean to hurt her, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.56,1:54:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你可以拥有完整的人生了\N{\fs40.9}You go live your life in full now,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.30,1:54:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 你为我们两个人而活\N{\fs40.9}all right? You live for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.54,1:54:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了\N{\fs40.9}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.34,1:55:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得足够仔细吗\N{\fs40.9}Are you watching closely?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.62,1:56:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它推到尽头去\N{\fs40.9}Put it down on the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.36,1:56:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真想想你的辉煌成就\N{\fs40.9}Take a minute to consider your achievement.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.94,1:56:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经告诉你 有个水手 \N{\fs40.9}I once told you about a sailor
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.66,1:56:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我描述过淹水的感受\N{\fs40.9}who described drowning to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.03,1:56:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 他说那感觉就像回家\N{\fs40.9}Yes, he said it was like going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.34,1:56:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撒谎了 \N{\fs40.9}I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.22,1:56:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 那痛苦至极\N{\fs40.9}He said it was agony.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.06,1:57:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德·波顿 今天 \N{\fs40.9}Alfred Borden, this day,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.26,1:57:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以国王和英格兰最高法庭的名义\N{\fs40.9}in the name of the king and the High Court of England,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.26,1:57:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将迎来死亡\N{\fs40.9}you will meet your end.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.30,1:57:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人在乎躲在台下的人\N{\fs40.9}No one cares about the man in the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.14,1:57:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特\N{\fs40.9}Cutter?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.52,1:57:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特\N{\fs40.9}Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.94,1:58:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么遗言吗\N{\fs40.9}Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.92,1:58:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,'咒语'\N{\fs40.9}Abracadabra.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.82,1:58:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是兄弟 是双胞胎\N{\fs40.9}A brother? A twin?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.39,1:58:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是法隆\N{\fs40.9}You were Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.26,1:58:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一直都是  - 不\N{\fs40.9}- The whole time? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.96,1:58:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是法隆\N{\fs40.9}We were both Fallon.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.37,1:59:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也都是波顿\N{\fs40.9}We were both Borden.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.64,1:59:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是躲进门的那个\N{\fs40.9}Were you the one who went into the box?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.68,1:59:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是出来的那个\N{\fs40.9}Or the one who came back out?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.68,1:59:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们轮换着来\N{\fs40.9}We took turns.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.79,1:59:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键在于我们交接的时候\N{\fs40.9}The trick is where we would swap.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.06,1:59:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特本来猜到的\N{\fs40.9}Cutter knew. Cutter knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.14,1:59:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我告诉他 这太简单了 太轻松了\N{\fs40.9}But I told him it was too simple, too easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.86,1:59:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40.9}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.04,1:59:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单 也许吧 但绝不轻松\N{\fs40.9}Simple, maybe, but not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.52,1:59:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人分享一份人生 根本一点也不轻松\N{\fs40.9}There's nothing easy about two men sharing one life.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.76,1:59:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白 怎么又流血了\N{\fs40.9}I don't understand, how it can be bleeding again?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.19,1:59:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那奥利维娅和你的妻子又是怎么回事\N{\fs40.9}Wha... What about Olivia and your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.99,2:00:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们各爱她们中的一个\N{\fs40.9}We each loved one of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.53,2:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱莎拉\N{\fs40.9}I loved Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.64,2:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爱奥利维娅\N{\fs40.9}He loved Olivia.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.44,2:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都各自享有一半的人生\N{\fs40.9}We each had half of a full life,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.74,2:00:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我们来说已经\N{\fs40.9}really, which was enough for us...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.74,2:00:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足够了\N{\fs40.9}...just.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.15,2:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对她们不是\N{\fs40.9}But not for them.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.76,2:00:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这就是牺牲 罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}See, sacrifice, Robert,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.88,2:00:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个好魔术必须付出的代价\N{\fs40.9}that's the price of a good trick.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.96,2:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你对此一无所知 不是吗\N{\fs40.9}You wouldn't know anything about that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.36,2:00:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也有过牺牲\N{\fs40.9}I've... I've made sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.62,2:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 真的\N{\fs40.9}- No. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.80,2:00:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窃取别人的成果根本不费吹灰之力\N{\fs40.9}It takes nothing to steal another man's work.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.97,2:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 我为之付出了一切\N{\fs40.9}Yeah, it takes everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.79,2:01:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 等等 我不\N{\fs40.9}No, no, wait, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.00,2:01:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这需要勇气\N{\fs40.9}It took courage.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.24,2:01:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每个晚上走进那台机器都需要勇气\N{\fs40.9}It took courage to climb into that machine every night,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.24,2:01:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 \N{\fs40.9}not knowing...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.84,2:01:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己会是掉落水箱的那个\N{\fs40.9}...if I'd be the man in the box...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.36,2:01:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是现身的那个\N{\fs40.9}...or in the prestige.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.78,2:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看看我为之付出的代价吗\N{\fs40.9}Do you want to see... ...what it cost me?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.20,2:01:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没看看自己身处何处吗 \N{\fs40.9}You didn't see where you are, did you?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.88,2:01:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呐 看呐\N{\fs40.9}Look. Look.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.17,2:01:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fs40.9}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.54,2:01:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你环游了半个世界\N{\fs40.9}You went halfway around the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.01,2:01:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了不少钱\N{\fs40.9}You spent a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.85,2:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却做出如此可怕的事情\N{\fs40.9}You did terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.38,2:02:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的惨不忍睹 罗伯特\N{\fs40.9}Really terrible things, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.06,2:02:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来却一场空\N{\fs40.9}And all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.38,2:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场空\N{\fs40.9}For nothing?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.63,2:02:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40.9}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.76,2:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从不明白\N{\fs40.9}You never understood...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.48,2:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做这一切是为了什么\N{\fs40.9}...why we did this.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.44,2:02:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众其实心里一清二楚\N{\fs40.9}The audience knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.14,2:02:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界很简单\N{\fs40.9}The world is simple.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.65,2:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却也很可悲\N{\fs40.9}It's miserable.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.60,2:02:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由始至终 永无止境\N{\fs40.9}Solid... Solid all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.49,2:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你有办法骗过他们\N{\fs40.9}But if you could fool them,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.89,2:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一秒\N{\fs40.9}even for a second...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.59,2:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勾起他们的好奇心\N{\fs40.9}...then you could make them wonder.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.13,2:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能看到真正特别的东西\N{\fs40.9}And then you... Then you got to see something very special.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.67,2:03:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真的一无所知\N{\fs40.9}You really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.64,2:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们付出所有的一切\N{\fs40.9}It was...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.02,2:03:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了他们脸上的表情而已\N{\fs40.9}...it was the look on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.17,2:03:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个魔术都由三个部分 或者说是三个步骤组成\N{\fs40.9}Every magic trick consists of three parts, or acts.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.44,2:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一部分叫"暗度陈仓"\N{\fs40.9}The first part is called "The pledge."
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.98,2:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师向你展示某个看似平常的物件\N{\fs40.9}The magician shows you something ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.02,2:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二部分叫做"风云变色"\N{\fs40.9}The second act is called "The turn."
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.08,2:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术师让那个看似平常的东西\N{\fs40.9}The magician takes the ordinary something
Dialogue: 0,2:03:50.22,2:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现出非同寻常的效果\N{\fs40.9}and makes it into something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.43,2:03:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但此时你还不会为之鼓掌\N{\fs40.9}But you wouldn't clap yet,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.42,2:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为把东西变没并没有什么了不起\N{\fs40.9}because making something disappear isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.24,2:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的是能再把它变回来\N{\fs40.9}You have to bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.94,2:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你肯定很想弄清其中奥义\N{\fs40.9}Now you're looking for the secret.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.31,2:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不会如愿的 因为\N{\fs40.9}But you won't find it, because,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.76,2:04:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 你并没有仔细观看\N{\fs40.9}of course, you're not really looking.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.15,2:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是真的想把它弄清楚\N{\fs40.9}You don't really want to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.39,2:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望被愚弄\N{\fs40.9}You want to be fooled.

